{"type":"message","id":"0fa24e45","parentId":"07d29937","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:53:48.115Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成了！让我总结一下这次升级的内容。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定！🦐 \n\n已经按 v3.0 规范重写，核心升级：\n\n| 模块 | 改进 |\n|------|------|\n| **评分** | 2维度（复杂度+不确定性），每维0-3分，总分0-6 |\n| **路由** | 0-1直接执行，2-3拆步骤存档，4-5spawn子代理，6拆多个子代理 |\n| **超时** | 30秒/60秒/max(60,总分×60)秒，10分钟兜底 |\n| **防卡死** | 每10秒产出检测 + 30秒无输出判卡死 + 2GB内存限制 |\n| **存档** | JSON格式 + 原子写入 + 自动恢复 |\n| **可观测性** | JSON Lines结构化日志 |\n\n这回应该不会再出现检查代码卡死的情况了——超时强制kill，连续失败3次标记BLOCKED等待人工介入。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":21529,"output":207,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21736,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775321625142,"responseId":"chatcmpl-db8a4ec0-bfb1-4f00-a43e-adce55ac4817"}}
