{"type":"message","id":"313be84c","parentId":"2126c180","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:58:19.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成！现在这个技能已经是v4.0了，包含了完整的上下文保护机制。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定 v4.0！🦐 \n\n新增的上下文保护模块：\n\n| 保护项 | 阈值 | 处理方式 |\n|--------|------|----------|\n| **会话压缩** | ≥50条消息 | 自动summarize，保留最近5条 |\n| **大文件读取** | >100KB分段，>1MB用shell | 不全文载入上下文 |\n| **长输出截断** | >10KB | 写临时文件，会话只显示1KB |\n| **子代理隔离** | spawn时 | 不继承父会话历史 |\n| **并发限制** | 最多3个任务 | FIFO排队 |\n\n现在这技能既能防卡死，又能防撑爆——完美解决你之前遇到的问题！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":25578,"output":168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25746,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775321896622,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f823091a-4306-476c-803b-7af143d982ea"}}
