{"type":"message","id":"089a4384","parentId":"8930d1a4","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:12:45.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成！把完整的实现指南也整合进技能里了。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定！🦐 \n\n技能已升级到 **v4.1**，新增了完整的**开发者实现指南**（伪代码）：\n\n| 模块 | 伪代码 |\n|------|--------|\n| 输出截断+存储 | ✅ handle_task_output() |\n| 并发限制+队列 | ✅ submit_task() + scheduler_loop() |\n| 内存限制+OOM重试 | ✅ spawn_subagent() + run_with_oom_retry() |\n| 自动Summarize | ✅ auto_summarize() 降级处理 |\n| 大文件分段读 | ✅ safe_read_file() |\n| 检查点+恢复 | ✅ step_task_execute() 原子写入 |\n\n现在这技能既是**执行规范**，又是**实现指南**，开发者可以直接对照着写了！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":85617,"output":169,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85786,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775322762471,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d0da13c9-ea34-4c7a-b05d-767f2e2b5ac7"}}
