{"type":"message","id":"e163f244","parentId":"7d4b1c11","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:21:18.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to implement the protection layer I designed earlier. Let me first summarize my implementation plan, then start实施.\n\nPreviously I said I would:\n1. Create a standalone protection module at `~/.openclaw/protection/`\n2. Multiple modules: limiter.js, timeout.js, truncation.js, memory.js, checkpoint.js, summarize.js, config.js\n3. Integration approach\n\nNow they want to start implementing it. Let me tell them my plan first before doing it.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 实施方案\n\n### 1. 创建独立保护层目录\n```\n~/.openclaw/protection/\n```\n\n### 2. 核心模块（按优先级实现）\n\n| 优先级 | 模块 | 功能 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| P0 | `limiter.js` | 并发限制 + 任务队列 |\n| P0 | `timeout.js` | 超时 + 无产出检测 |\n| P1 | `truncation.js` | 输出截断存储到文件 |\n| P1 | `memory.js` | setrlimit 内存限制 |\n| P2 | `checkpoint.js` | 检查点 + 自动恢复 |\n| P2 | `summarize.js` | 会话自动压缩 |\n\n### 3. 主入口\n- `index.js` 统一导出，拦截所有 exec/spawn 操作\n\n### 4. 接入 OpenClaw\n- 方案：创建一个 OpenClaw 插件或扩展配置，让系统加载这个保护层\n\n---\n\n**现在开始写吗？** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":569,"output":308,"cacheRead":90240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91117,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775323257675,"responseId":"019d5982964159dc0f83609547dcea40"}}
