{"type":"message","id":"c7af4ae4","parentId":"32bfc54b","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:23:57.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"目录创建成功，现在写存档。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5985b0c7061ed2361ebd32609b50","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 任务进度\n\n## 实施 OpenCLaw 保护层\n- 状态: 进行中\n- 创建时间: 2026-04-05 01:23\n- 预计步骤: 9\n\n### 步骤 1: 创建目录结构 ✅\n- 完成时间: 01:23\n- 产出: ~/.openclaw/protection/ 目录\n\n### 步骤 2: 实现 limiter.js 🔄\n- 状态: 待开始\n\n### 步骤 3: 实现 timeout.js\n- 状态: 待开始\n\n### 步骤 4: 实现 truncation.js\n- 状态: 待开始\n\n### 步骤 5: 实现 memory.js\n- 状态: 待开始\n\n### 步骤 6: 实现 checkpoint.js\n- 状态: 待开始\n\n### 步骤 7: 实现 summarize.js\n- 状态: 待开始\n\n### 步骤 8: 实现主入口 index.js\n- 状态: 待开始\n\n### 步骤 9: 写存档记录\n- 状态: 待开始\n\n### 下一步: 步骤 2","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/self-improving/task-progress.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":324,"output":282,"cacheRead":92288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92894,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775323418194,"responseId":"019d59858c3264478ff71451e7b4b6e1"}}
