{"type":"message","id":"d88e9190","parentId":"9dbc217b","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:46:43.473Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Now I've updated the memory to be more prominent and added a quick reference table. The key change is:\n\n1. Made \"核心铁律\" the top priority - must score before doing anything\n2. Added a quick reference table for fast decision making\n3. Added a reminder at the end: \"记住：每次都要先评分！\"\n\nFrom now on, every time the user gives me a task, I should score it first and show the result.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n记住了！🦐 \n\n已更新到记忆，强调：\n- **核心铁律**：永远先评分，不评分不执行\n- **快速参考表**：常见任务的预估分数和路由\n- **记住**：每次都要先评分！\n\n以后收到任务，我会直接显示评分结果再执行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":109953,"output":155,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110108,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775324800257,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a64b63f5-0639-45bd-92ba-47df20b094eb"}}
