{"type":"message","id":"658a0cdf","parentId":"a46c48b6","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:47:22.360Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我继续接入OpenClaw。\n\n根据 task-weight-estimator v4.1 评分：\n\n这个任务是\"接入 OpenClaw\"，复杂度：2-3分（配置+测试），不确定性：1-2分（涉及系统配置），总分：3-5分，路由：spawn子代理或拆步骤存档\n\n让我按步骤来，先评分，再执行。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 评分\n\n| 维度 | 评分 |\n|------|------|\n| 复杂度 | 2-3分（配置修改 + 测试） |\n| 不确定性 | 1-2分（修改配置） |\n| **总分** | **3-5分** |\n| **路由** | **拆步骤存档** |\n\n---\n\n## 实施步骤\n\n```\n步骤1: 查找 OpenClaw 配置文件位置\n步骤2: 创建保护层加载配置\n步骤3: 配置环境变量\n步骤4: 测试加载\n步骤5: 存档\n```\n\n---\n\n开始！\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d599b41301433fce68521be8b492d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/ 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":17608,"output":236,"cacheRead":92416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110260,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775324826234,"responseId":"019d599b0b1dda51f46ce86abe273c2f"}}
