{"type":"message","id":"0a43353e","parentId":"673fafea","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:47:56.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了配置。现在我需要找到如何接入保护层。\n\n看起来OpenClaw有 hooks 和 plugins 配置。我可以通过以下方式接入：\n\n1. **环境变量**：添加保护层相关的环境变量配置\n2. **创建插件**：在 plugins.entries 中添加保护层\n3. **创建 hook**：在 hooks 中添加\n\n让我先创建一个简单的配置文件，用于保护层，然后更新 openclaw.json 添加相关配置。\n\n实际上，更简单的方法是：\n1. 创建一个环境变量配置文件 (.env)\n2. 让保护层作为独立模块，在需要时被调用\n\n让我先创建配置文件，然后更新存档。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d599b0896ff92d54cd35d368551ec","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# OpenClaw 保护层配置文件\n# ~/.openclaw/protection/config.env\n\n# 并发限制\nOPENCLAW_MAX_CONCURRENT=3\nOPENCLAW_QUEUE_MAX_SIZE=30\n\n# 超时配置\nOPENCLAW_DIRECT_TIMEOUT=30000\nOPENCLAW_STEP_TIMEOUT=60000\nOPENCLAW_GLOBAL_TIMEOUT=600000\nOPENCLAW_NO_OUTPUT_TIMEOUT=30000\n\n# 输出截断\nOPENCLAW_MAX_OUTPUT_KB=10\nOPENCLAW_OUTPUT_DIR=/tmp/openclaw\n\n# 内存限制 (MB)\nOPENCLAW_MEMORY_SOFT_MB=2000\nOPENCLAW_MEMORY_HARD_MB=2500\nOPENCLAW_MAX_RETRIES=3\n\n# 会话自动压缩\nOPENCLAW_SUMMARIZE_THRESHOLD=50\nOPENCLAW_SUMMARIZE_RESERVE=5\nOPENCLAW_AUTO_SUMMARIZE=true\nOPENCLAW_SUMMARIZE_COOLDOWN=120000\n\n# 检查点\nOPENCLAW_CHECKPOINT_DIR=/tmp/openclaw/checkpoints","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/protection/config.env"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":6424,"output":385,"cacheRead":106112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112921,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775324848901,"responseId":"019d599adce4614a15fec6e89ee090fe"}}
