{"type":"message","id":"d49b2c06","parentId":"49748ae7","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:48:18.176Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我写存档，然后告诉用户完成了。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b470aeccf49049cca5d5e0e2","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 任务进度\n\n## 接入 OpenClaw 保护层\n- 状态: ✅ 已完成\n- 创建时间: 2026-04-05 01:47\n\n### 步骤 1: 查找配置文件 ✅\n- 产出: ~/.openclaw/config.json, ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\n### 步骤 2: 创建保护层配置 ✅\n- 产出: ~/.openclaw/protection/config.env\n- 内容: 所有环境变量配置\n\n### 步骤 3: 创建加载器 ✅\n- 产出: ~/.openclaw/protection/loader.js\n- 功能: 自动加载模块 + 应用配置\n\n### 步骤 4: 存档 ✅\n\n---\n\n## 最终文件结构\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/protection/\n├── index.js          # 主入口\n├── loader.js         # 加载器（自动初始化）\n├── config.env        # 配置文件\n├── limiter.js        # 并发限制+队列\n├── timeout.js        # 超时+无产出检测\n├── truncation.js     # 输出截断存储\n├── memory.js         # 内存限制+OOM\n├── checkpoint.js     # 检查点+恢复\n└── summarize.js      # 会话自动压缩\n```\n\n## 启用方式\n\n1. **方式一**：设置环境变量\n   ```\n   OPENCLAW_PROTECTION_ENABLED=true\n   ```\n\n2. **方式二**：创建标记文件\n   ```\n   touch ~/.openclaw/protection/enabled\n   ```\n\n3. **方式三**：在代码中导入\n   ```javascript\n   import { init } from './protection/loader.js';\n   const protection = await init();\n   ```\n\n## 状态查询\n\n```javascript\nimport { init } from './protection/loader.js';\nconst p = await init();\nconsole.log(p.getStatus());\n```","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/self-improving/task-progress.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":113882,"output":428,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114310,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775324890342,"responseId":"chatcmpl-00a83f89-4e9b-49e0-a802-1ed694a33a0c"}}
