{"type":"message","id":"1816d5e8","parentId":"0464e1ad","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:49:53.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成了，给用户汇报结果。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 保护层已启用！\n\n### 状态检查\n\n| 模块 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| **limiter** | ✅ 并发限制 3，队列0 |\n| **timeout** | ✅ 监控0个任务 |\n| **truncation** | ✅ 输出目录 /tmp/openclaw |\n| **memory** | ✅ 内存限制 2GB，重试3次 |\n| **summarizer** | ✅ 阈值50条，自动开启 |\n\n---\n\n**保护层已就绪！** 🦐\n\n现在你可以派任务给我，我会：\n1. 先评分\n2. 执行时自动保护（超时、内存、输出截断等）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":115323,"output":149,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115472,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775324990480,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5f8b7615-ef5c-4ccc-b9db-7afce9c71e82"}}
