{"type":"message","id":"154d8ede","parentId":"ee57b7a7","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:50:34.967Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to introduce/present the protection layer that we've created and enabled. Let me give a comprehensive summary.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 🛡️ OpenClaw 保护层介绍\n\n### 是什么？\n一个独立的高鲁棒执行保护系统，防止任务卡死、上下文撑爆、内存溢出等问题。\n\n### 核心模块\n\n| 模块 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| **limiter** | 并发限制（最多3个任务）+ 任务队列 |\n| **timeout** | 超时控制 + 无产出检测（卡死判定） |\n| **truncation** | 输出截断（>10KB存文件）+ 24h自动清理 |\n| **memory** | 内存限制（2GB）+ OOM自动重试 |\n| **checkpoint** | 检查点存档 + 崩溃自动恢复 |\n| **summarize** | 会话自动压缩（≥50条消息） |\n\n### 使用流程\n\n```\n收到任务\n   ↓\n【评分】task-weight-estimator v4.1 (0-6分)\n   ↓\n【路由】直接执行 / 拆步骤 / spawn子代理\n   ↓\n【保护执行】\n  - 自动超时控制\n  - 自动输出截断  \n  - 自动内存限制\n  - 自动存档\n   ↓\n【完成】\n```\n\n### 配置文件\n- `~/.openclaw/protection/config.env` - 所有可配置项\n- `~/.openclaw/protection/enabled` - 启用标记\n\n### 状态查询\n```javascript\nimport { init } from './protection/loader.js';\nconst p = await init();\nconsole.log(p.getStatus());\n```\n\n---\n\n**保护层已启用，有任务派给我吗？** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5571,"output":354,"cacheRead":109952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115877,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775325015916,"responseId":"019d599d3bdeda416a3b8ae0b9766549"}}
