{"type":"message","id":"90eacdf2","parentId":"c9504256","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:52:57.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问保护层是否会检测当前已使用的上下文容量并进行应对。让我检查一下现有代码。\n\n实际上，目前的保护层中：\n1. summarize.js - 会按消息数量（50条）触发自动压缩\n2. 但它没有直接检测\"上下文容量\"（token数量）\n\nOpenClaw 本身应该有自己的上下文管理机制（在 agent-runner.runtime 中有 memory-flush 相关代码）。\n\n我应该诚实回答：\n- 当前保护层按**消息数量**检测（50条）\n- 没有直接检测**token数量**或**字符数**\n- OpenClaw 底层有自己的上下文管理（memory-flush），但保护层可以与之配合\n\n需要改进：可以加入基于token/字符的检测。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 当前状态\n\n| 检测项 | 状态 |\n|--------|------|\n| **消息数量** | ✅ 已实现（≥50条触发压缩） |\n| **Token数量** | ❌ 未实现 |\n| **字符数** | ❌ 未实现 |\n| **OpenClaw底层** | ✅ 有 memory-flush（context limit） |\n\n---\n\n### 说明\n\n当前保护层的 `summarize.js` 是按**消息条数**触发（50条），但没有直接检测：\n- Token数量\n- 字符数\n- 上下文使用百分比\n\n**好消息**：OpenClaw 底层已有 `memory-flush` 机制（在你检查源码时看到的），当上下文接近上限时会自动压缩。\n\n---\n\n### 需要我改进吗？\n\n可以加：\n1. **基于字符数检测**（如 > 100KB）\n2. **基于Token估算**（调用模型前检查）\n3. **与OpenClaw底层联动**（共享状态）\n\n**要加上吗？** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2494,"output":356,"cacheRead":114560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117410,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775325158681,"responseId":"019d599f7dc0a3c994b57a3e81ba14b5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"44b43c45","parentId":"90eacdf2","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:59:29.349Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 01:59 GMT+8] 学习：# OpenClaw 改进方案最优解：完整伪代码实现\n\n> 本方案假设 OpenClaw 已具备：超时（timeoutMs）、无产出检测（noOutputTimeoutMs）、子代理 spawn、底层 memory-flush。以下伪代码为**增量增强**，可直接嵌入现有架构。\n\n---\n\n## 一、上下文保护模块（context_protector.js / .py）\n\n### 1.1 多维度检测与自动压缩\n\n```javascript\n// 配置\nconst CONFIG = {\n msgThreshold: 50, // 消息条数阈值\n charThreshold: 100 * 1024, // 100 KB\n tokenUsageRatio: 0.8, // 80%\n tokenLimit: 128 * 1024, // 128K，根据模型调整\n checkIntervalMs: 30000, // 30秒轮询底层\n cooldownSec: 120, // 压缩冷却期\n};\n\nlet state = {\n messages: [], // 会话历史\n totalChars: 0,\n lastSummarize: 0,\n backupFile: \"history_backup.json\"\n};\n\n// 估算 token（轻量，不调用模型）\nfunction estimateTokens(text) {\n const chinese = (text.match(/[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]/g) || []).length;\n const other = text.length - chinese;\n return Math.ceil(chinese / 1.5 + other / 4);\n}\n\n// 从底层获取真实使用率（若 OpenClaw 暴露）\nfunction getRealContextUsage() {\n if (typeof openclaw !== 'undefined' && openclaw.getContextStats) {\n return openclaw.getContextStats(); // { usedTokens, limit, percent }\n }\n return null;\n}\n\n// 触发压缩\nasync function autoSummarize(reason) {\n if (Date.now() - state.lastSummarize < CONFIG.cooldownSec * 1000) return;\n\n // 备份\n await backupHistory(state.messages, state.backupFile);\n\n try {\n let summary;\n // 优先调用外部 summarize API\n if (typeof summarizeAPI === 'function') {\n summary = await summarizeAPI(state.messages.slice(0, -5));\n }\n if (!summary) throw new Error('API failed');\n\n // 压缩：摘要 + 最近5条完整消息\n state.messages = [\n { role: 'system', content: `[历史摘要] ${summary}` },\n ...state.messages.slice(-5)\n ];\n logEvent('auto_summarize', { reason, oldCount: state.messages.length, newCount: state.messages.length });\n } catch (err) {\n // 降级：保留最近20条 + 提取关键信息\n const critical = extractCriticalInfo(state.messages);\n const kept = state.messages.slice(-20);\n kept.unshift({ role: 'system', content: `[关键信息] ${critical}` });\n state.messages = kept;\n logEvent('summarize_fallback', { reason, error: err.message });\n }\n state.totalChars = state.messages.reduce((sum, m) => sum + (m.content?.length || 0), 0);\n state.lastSummarize = Date.now();\n}\n\n// 每次新增消息时调用\nfunction onNewMessage(message) {\n state.messages.push(message);\n state.totalChars += message.content.length;\n\n let needSummarize = false;\n let reason = '';\n\n // 1. 消息条数\n if (state.messages.length >= CONFIG.msgThreshold) {\n needSummarize = true;\n reason = 'message_count';\n }\n // 2. 字符数\n else if (state.totalChars >= CONFIG.charThreshold) {\n needSummarize = true;\n reason = 'char_threshold';\n }\n // 3. 估算 token（如果没有真实数据）\n else {\n const real = getRealContextUsage();\n if (real && real.percent >= CONFIG.tokenUsageRatio) {\n needSummarize = true;\n reason = 'token_usage_real';\n } else if (!real) {\n const historyText = state.messages.map(m => m.content).join('\\n');\n const estimated = estimateTokens(historyText);\n if (estimated / CONFIG.tokenLimit >= CONFIG.tokenUsageRatio) {\n needSummarize = true;\n reason = 'token_usage_estimated';\n }\n }\n }\n\n if (needSummarize) {\n autoSummarize(reason);\n }\n}\n\n// 定期轮询底层（每30秒）\nsetInterval(() => {\n const real = getRealContextUsage();\n if (real && real.percent >= CONFIG.tokenUsageRatio) {\n autoSummarize('periodic_poll');\n }\n}, CONFIG.checkIntervalMs);\n\n// 回滚命令\nfunction rollbackSummarize() {\n if (exists(state.backupFile)) {\n state.messages = restoreHistory(state.backupFile);\n state.totalChars = state.messages.reduce((sum, m) => sum + (m.content?.length || 0), 0);\n logEvent('rollback_summarize');\n return true;\n }\n return false;\n}\n```\n\n### 1.2 大文件分段读取（safe_read_file.js）\n\n```javascript\nasync function safeReadFile(filepath, maxSizeKb = 100, maxMmapMb = 100) {\n const stats = await fs.stat(filepath);\n const size = stats.size;\n\n // 特殊文件（/proc, /dev）拒绝\n if (filepath.startsWith('/proc/') || filepath.startsWith('/dev/')) {\n throw new Error('Cannot read special file');\n }\n\n // 超大文件：使用 shell 按需提取\n if (size > maxMmapMb * 1024 * 1024) {\n return await extractWithShell(filepath); // head -n 100, grep, etc.\n }\n\n // 内存检查\n const memFree = os.freemem();\n if (memFree < 256 * 1024 * 1024) {\n console.warn('Low memory, waiting...');\n await waitForMemory(512 * 1024 * 1024, 30000);\n }\n\n if (size <= maxSizeKb * 1024) {\n return await fs.readFile(filepath, 'utf8');\n }\n\n // 分段读取\n let chunks = [];\n const fd = await fs.open(filepath, 'r');\n const buffer = Buffer.alloc(maxSizeKb * 1024);\n let bytesRead;\n while ((bytesRead = await fd.read(buffer, 0, buffer.length, null)) !== 0) {\n chunks.push(buffer.slice(0, bytesRead));\n await sleep(0); // 让出事件循环\n }\n await fd.close();\n return Buffer.concat(chunks).toString('utf8');\n}\n```\n\n### 1.3 输出截断与存储（output_truncator.js）\n\n```javascript\nclass OutputTruncator {\n constructor(taskId, maxKb = 10) {\n this.taskId = taskId;\n this.maxBytes = maxKb * 1024;\n this.buffer = '';\n this.total = 0;\n this.tempFile = null;\n this.overflow = false;\n this.tailBuffer = '';\n }\n\n write(chunk) {\n const line = chunk.toString();\n this.total += line.length;\n\n if (!this.overflow && this.total <= this.maxBytes) {\n this.buffer += line;\n process.stdout.write(line); // 实时显示\n return;\n }\n\n if (!this.overflow) {\n // 首次超限：创建临时文件，保留最后1KB\n this.overflow = true;\n this.tempFile = fs.createWriteStream(`/tmp/openclaw/task_${this.taskId}.out`);\n // 提取尾部（UTF-8安全）\n let tailBytes = this.buffer.slice(-1024);\n while (!isValidUtf8(tailBytes)) tailBytes = tailBytes.slice(1);\n this.tailBuffer = tailBytes;\n this.tempFile.write(this.buffer);\n this.buffer = this.tailBuffer;\n }\n\n if (this.tempFile) {\n try {\n this.tempFile.write(line);\n } catch (err) {\n console.warn(`Output truncation failed: ${err.message}`);\n this.tempFile = null;\n }\n }\n }\n\n close() {\n if (this.overflow && this.tempFile) {\n this.tempFile.end();\n console.log(`[Hint] Full output saved to ${this.tempFile.path}, last 1KB:\\n${this.tailBuffer}`);\n } else if (this.total > this.maxBytes && !this.tempFile) {\n console.warn('[Warning] Output truncation failed (disk full/permission)');\n }\n // 安排24小时后删除\n scheduleDeletion(this.tempFile?.path, 24 * 3600);\n }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 二、全局并发队列（persistent_queue.js）\n\n```javascript\nconst sqlite3 = require('sqlite3').verbose();\nconst db = new sqlite3.Database('task_queue.sqlite');\n\ndb.run(`CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS tasks (\n id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n spec TEXT,\n submitted_at INTEGER\n)`);\n\nclass PersistentQueue {\n constructor(maxConcurrent = 3, maxSize = 30) {\n this.maxConcurrent = maxConcurrent;\n this.maxSize = maxSize;\n this.active = 0;\n this.lock = new Mutex();\n }\n\n async push(taskSpec) {\n const count = await this.count();\n if (count >= this.maxSize) {\n throw { code: 429, message: 'QUEUE_FULL' };\n }\n const id = generateId();\n await db.run('INSERT INTO tasks VALUES (?, ?, ?)', id, JSON.stringify(taskSpec), Date.now());\n this.schedule();\n return id;\n }\n\n async pop() {\n const row = await db.get('SELECT * FROM tasks ORDER BY submitted_at LIMIT 1');\n if (row) {\n await db.run('DELETE FROM tasks WHERE id = ?', row.id);\n return { id: row.id, spec: JSON.parse(row.spec), submittedAt: row.submitted_at };\n }\n return null;\n }\n\n async schedule() {\n if (this.active >= this.maxConcurrent) return;\n const task = await this.pop();\n if (!task) return;\n this.active++;\n this.execute(task).finally(() => {\n this.active--;\n this.schedule();\n });\n }\n\n async execute(task) {\n try {\n await runWithTimeout(task.spec);\n } catch (err) {\n logEvent('task_failed', { taskId: task.id, error: err.message });\n }\n }\n\n async count() {\n const row = await db.get('SELECT COUNT(*) as c FROM tasks');\n return row.c;\n }\n\n // 清理排队超时（5分钟）\n async cleanTimeout(timeoutMs = 300000) {\n const now = Date.now();\n await db.run('DELETE FROM tasks WHERE submitted_at < ?', now - timeoutMs);\n }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、检查点与自动恢复（checkpoint.js）\n\n```javascript\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst fs = require('fs').promises;\n\nasync function atomicWriteJSON(filepath, data) {\n data.checksum = crypto.createHash('sha256').update(JSON.stringify(data)).digest('hex');\n const tmp = filepath + '.tmp';\n await fs.writeFile(tmp, JSON.stringify(data));\n await fs.fsync(tmp);\n await fs.rename(tmp, filepath);\n await fs.copyFile(filepath, filepath + '.bak');\n}\n\nasync function loadCheckpoint(filepath) {\n try {\n const data = JSON.parse(await fs.readFile(filepath, 'utf8'));\n const checksum = data.checksum;\n delete data.checksum;\n const expected = crypto.createHash('sha256').update(JSON.stringify(data)).digest('hex');\n if (checksum !== expected) throw new Error('Checksum mismatch');\n return data;\n } catch (err) {\n console.warn(`Checkpoint corrupted: ${err.message}, trying backup`);\n try {\n return JSON.parse(await fs.readFile(filepath + '.bak', 'utf8'));\n } catch {\n return null;\n }\n }\n}\n\nasync function stepTaskExecute(task, steps) {\n const checkpointFile = `/var/openclaw/checkpoints/${task.id}.json`;\n let state = await loadCheckpoint(checkpointFile);\n let start = state ? state.lastCompletedStep + 1 : 0;\n\n for (let i = start; i < steps.length; i++) {\n try {\n await executeStep(steps[i]);\n await atomicWriteJSON(checkpointFile, {\n taskId: task.id,\n lastCompletedStep: i,\n timestamp: Date.now(),\n version: 1\n });\n } catch (err) {\n console.warn(`Step ${i} failed, task paused`);\n return;\n }\n }\n // 任务完成，删除检查点\n await fs.unlink(checkpointFile).catch(() => {});\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、子代理内存限制与 OOM 重试（subagent_oom.js）\n\n```javascript\nconst { spawn } = require('child_process');\nconst resource = require('resource');\n\nfunction spawnWithMemoryLimit(cmd, args, softMb = 2000, hardMb = 2500) {\n const proc = spawn(cmd, args, {\n detached: true,\n stdio: 'pipe',\n preexec: () => {\n // 限制地址空间\n resource.setrlimit(resource.RLIMIT_AS, softMb * 1024 * 1024, hardMb * 1024 * 1024);\n // 限制 RSS（若支持）\n try {\n resource.setrlimit(resource.RLIMIT_RSS, softMb * 1024 * 1024, hardMb * 1024 * 1024);\n } catch (e) {}\n }\n });\n return proc;\n}\n\nasync function runWithOomRetry(task, maxRetries = 3) {\n let retries = 0;\n while (retries <= maxRetries) {\n const proc = spawnWithMemoryLimit(task.cmd, task.args);\n const exitCode = await new Promise((resolve) => {\n proc.on('close', resolve);\n proc.on('error', resolve);\n });\n const isOom = (exitCode === 137 || exitCode === 9) && await peakMemoryExceeded(task.id, 2000);\n if (!isOom) return;\n retries++;\n if (retries <= maxRetries) {\n const delay = Math.pow(2, retries - 1) * 1000; // 1s,2s,4s\n console.warn(`OOM, retry ${retries}/${maxRetries} after ${delay}ms`);\n await sleep(delay);\n }\n }\n console.error(`Task ${task.id} OOM after ${maxRetries} retries, frozen`);\n await markFrozen(task.id);\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、熔断器与限流（circuit_breaker.js）\n\n```javascript\nclass CircuitBreaker {\n constructor(name, options = {}) {\n this.name = name;\n this.failureThreshold = options.failureThreshold || 5;\n this.timeoutSec = options.timeoutSec || 30;\n this.halfOpenSuccesses = options.halfOpenSuccesses || 3;\n this.state = 'CLOSED'; // CLOSED, OPEN, HALF_OPEN\n this.failures = 0;\n this.lastFailure = 0;\n this.successesInHalf = 0;\n }\n\n async call(fn) {\n if (this.state === 'OPEN') {\n if (Date.now() - this.lastFailure < this.timeoutSec * 1000) {\n throw new Error(`Circuit breaker ${this.name} is OPEN`);\n }\n this.state = 'HALF_OPEN';\n this.successesInHalf = 0;\n }\n\n try {\n const result = await fn();\n if (this.state === 'HALF_OPEN') {\n this.successesInHalf++;\n if (this.successesInHalf >= this.halfOpenSuccesses) {\n this.state = 'CLOSED';\n this.failures = 0;\n }\n }\n return result;\n } catch (err) {\n this.failures++;\n this.lastFailure = Date.now();\n if (this.failures >= this.failureThreshold) {\n this.state = 'OPEN';\n }\n throw err;\n }\n }\n}\n\n// 全局限流器（令牌桶）\nclass RateLimiter {\n constructor(tokensPerSec = 2, maxTokens = 10) {\n this.tokens = maxTokens;\n this.maxTokens = maxTokens;\n this.rate = tokensPerSec;\n this.lastRefill = Date.now();\n }\n\n acquire() {\n const now = Date.now();\n const elapsed = (now - this.lastRefill) / 1000;\n this.tokens = Math.min(this.maxTokens, this.tokens + elapsed * this.rate);\n this.lastRefill = now;\n if (this.tokens >= 1) {\n this.tokens -= 1;\n return true;\n }\n return false;\n }\n}\n\n// 动态降级并发度（基于失败率）\nlet currentConcurrency = 3;\nlet originalConcurrency = 3;\nlet failureWindow = [];\n\nsetInterval(() => {\n const now = Date.now();\n failureWindow = failureWindow.filter(t => now - t < 5 * 60 * 1000);\n const rate = failureWindow.length / (5 * 60); // 每分钟失败数\n if (rate > 0.5) { // 每分钟超过0.5次失败 => 失败率 > 50%? 更准确：按任务数比例\n currentConcurrency = Math.max(1, Math.floor(currentConcurrency / 2));\n console.warn(`High failure rate, reducing concurrency to ${currentConcurrency}`);\n } else {\n currentConcurrency = Math.min(originalConcurrency, currentConcurrency + 0.5);\n }\n}, 5 * 60 * 1000);\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、健康自愈（watchdog.js）\n\n```javascript\nlet lastLoopTime = Date.now();\n\n// 主循环每次迭代调用\nfunction updateLoopHeartbeat() {\n lastLoopTime = Date.now();\n}\n\n// 独立监控协程\nsetInterval(() => {\n const now = Date.now();\n if (now - lastLoopTime > 15000) { // 15秒无更新\n console.error('Main loop stuck, aborting to trigger systemd restart');\n process.abort();\n }\n}, 10000);\n\n// 暴露健康端点（如果使用 HTTP）\napp.get('/health', (req, res) => {\n const stats = {\n queueLength: queue.size(),\n activeTasks: activeCount,\n memoryMB: process.memoryUsage().rss / 1024 / 1024,\n lastLoopHeartbeat: lastLoopTime,\n circuitBreakers: Object.fromEntries(circuitBreakers.map(cb => [cb.name, cb.state]))\n };\n const healthy = stats.queueLength < 100 && stats.memoryMB < 1800;\n res.status(healthy ? 200 : 503).json(stats);\n});\n\n// systemd 服务文件片段\n// [Service]\n// Restart=always\n// RestartSec=10\n```\n\n---\n\n## 七、结构化日志（logger.js）\n\n```javascript\nconst winston = require('winston');\nconst DailyRotateFile = require('winston-daily-rotate-file');\n\nconst logger = winston.createLogger({\n level: 'info',\n format: winston.format.json(),\n transports: [\n new DailyRotateFile({\n filename: '/var/log/openclaw/events-%DATE%.log',\n datePattern: 'YYYY-MM-DD',\n maxSize: '100m',\n maxFiles: '10'\n })\n ]\n});\n\n// 限速器\nlet logCount = 0;\nsetInterval(() => { logCount = 0; }, 1000);\n\nfunction logEvent(eventType, meta = {}) {\n if (logCount >= 100) return; // 每秒最多100条\n logCount++;\n const entry = { timestamp: new Date().toISOString(), event: eventType, ...meta };\n logger.info(entry);\n // 关键事件写入 syslog\n if (['task_timeout', 'task_oom', 'circuit_open', 'self_abort'].includes(eventType)) {\n require('syslog').log('warning', `OpenClaw: ${eventType} ${JSON.stringify(meta)}`);\n }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 八、集成点（与现有 OpenClaw 对接）\n\n1. **在任务执行入口**：包裹 `OutputTruncator`。\n2. **在消息处理循环**：调用 `onNewMessage()`。\n3. **在 spawn 子代理前**：调用 `runWithOomRetry()` 而非直接 spawn。\n4. **在任务调度器**：使用 `PersistentQueue` 替代简单的数组队列。\n5. **在长时间任务（拆步骤）**：使用 `stepTaskExecute` 并写入检查点。\n6. **在启动时**：调用 `loadCheckpoint` 恢复未完成任务。\n7. **对外部 API（如 summarize）**：使用 `CircuitBreaker` 包装。\n8. **在主入口**：启动健康监控协程和日志轮转。\n\n---\n\n## 九、验证清单（实现后测试）\n\n- [ ] 模拟任务输出 1MB 日志 → 截断到 10KB，剩余写入文件，不卡终端。\n- [ ] 提交 20 个任务 → 只有 3 个同时运行，其余排队，队列持久化。\n- [ ] 会话消息达到 50 条或 100KB → 自动压缩，摘要或降级。\n- [ ] 子代理内存超 2GB → 被 kill，重试 3 次后退避冻结。\n- [ ] 主循环死锁 → 15 秒后主动 abort，systemd 重启。\n- [ ] 外部 summarize API 连续失败 5 次 → 熔断 30 秒，半开后连续成功 3 次恢复。\n- [ ] 任务执行到一半进程崩溃 → 重启后从检查点恢复。\n\n---\n\n**以上伪代码已覆盖所有增强点，可直接由 OpenClaw 开发者按模块实现。** 如需某一模块的具体语言实现（如 Python 版），可告知。"}],"timestamp":1775325569343}}
{"type":"message","id":"315f1d71","parentId":"44b43c45","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:01:06.301Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我学习这个新的改进方案。这是对之前 v4.1 规范的补充，增加了：\n\n1. 多维度检测（消息数+字符数+token使用率）\n2. 大文件分段读取（safeReadFile）\n3. 输出截断与存储（OutputTruncator）\n4. 持久化队列（SQLite）\n5. 检查点与恢复（已有checkpoint.js）\n6. 子代理内存限制与OOM重试（已有memory.js）\n7. 熔断器与限流（新增）\n8. 健康自愈（watchdog）\n9. 结构化日志（logger）\n10. 集成点清单\n\n让我把这个新方案整合到技能里。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n收到！让我把这个**完整增强方案**整合进保护层：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d59a6978bf71cc1d7e4a3e34cf481","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * OpenCLaw 保护层 - 上下文保护模块 (context_protector.js)\n * \n * 功能：\n * - 多维度检测（消息数+字符数+Token使用率）\n * - 自动压缩（API优先，降级裁剪）\n * - 定期轮询底层检测\n * - 回滚机制\n */\n\nimport * as fs from 'fs';\nimport * as path from 'path';\nimport * as os from 'os';\n\nclass ContextProtector {\n  constructor(options = {}) {\n    this.msgThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_MSG_THRESHOLD || '50');\n    this.charThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHAR_THRESHOLD || '102400'); // 100KB\n    this.tokenRatioThreshold = parseFloat(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_RATIO || '0.8');\n    this.tokenLimit = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_LIMIT || '131072'); // 128K\n    this.checkIntervalMs = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHECK_INTERVAL || '30000');\n    this.cooldownSec = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_COOLDOWN_SEC || '120');\n    \n    this.messages = [];\n    this.totalChars = 0;\n    this.lastSummarize = 0;\n    this.backupDir = path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'openclaw', 'history_backup');\n    this.ensureBackupDir();\n    \n    this.startPeriodicCheck();\n  }\n\n  ensureBackupDir() {\n    if (!fs.existsSync(this.backupDir)) {\n      fs.mkdirSync(this.backupDir, { recursive: true });\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 估算 token（轻量方法）\n   */\n  estimateTokens(text) {\n    const chinese = (text.match(/[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]/g) || []).length;\n    const other = text.length - chinese;\n    return Math.ceil(chinese / 1.5 + other / 4);\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 从底层获取真实使用率\n   */\n  getRealContextUsage() {\n    // TODO: 与 OpenClaw 底层联动\n    // if (typeof openclaw !== 'undefined' && openclaw.getContextStats) {\n    //   return openclaw.getContextStats();\n    // }\n    return null;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 触发压缩\n   */\n  async autoSummarize(reason) {\n    if (Date.now() - this.lastSummarize < this.cooldownSec * 1000) {\n      return { skipped: true, reason: 'cooldown' };\n    }\n\n    // 备份\n    await this.backupHistory();\n\n    try {\n      let summary = null;\n      \n      // 优先调用外部 API\n      // if (typeof summarizeAPI === 'function') {\n      //   summary = await summarizeAPI(this.messages.slice(0, -5));\n      // }\n      \n      // 模拟摘要生成（实际应调用 API）\n      if (!summary) {\n        const recent = this.messages.slice(-10);\n        summary = `[会话摘要] 共 ${this.messages.length} 条消息，关键内容: ${recent.map(m => m.content?.slice(0, 50)).join(' | ')}`;\n      }\n\n      this.messages = [\n        { role: 'system', content: `[历史摘要] ${summary}` },\n        ...this.messages.slice(-5)\n      ];\n      \n      this.recalcChars();\n      this.lastSummarize = Date.now();\n      \n      return { success: true, reason, oldCount: this.messages.length + 5, newCount: this.messages.length };\n      \n    } catch (err) {\n      // 降级：保留最近20条 + 关键信息\n      const critical = this.extractCriticalInfo();\n      const kept = this.messages.slice(-20);\n      kept.unshift({ role: 'system', content: `[关键信息] ${critical}` });\n      this.messages = kept;\n      this.recalcChars();\n      this.lastSummarize = Date.now();\n      \n      return { fallback: true, reason, error: err.message };\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 提取关键信息\n   */\n  extractCriticalInfo() {\n    const critical = [];\n    \n    for (const msg of this.messages) {\n      if (msg.role === 'system' && msg.content?.includes('任务')) {\n        critical.push(msg.content.slice(0, 200));\n      }\n    }\n    \n    const recent = this.messages.slice(-5);\n    for (const msg of recent) {\n      if (msg.content?.length > 0) {\n        critical.push(`[最近] ${msg.content.slice(0, 80)}`);\n      }\n    }\n    \n    return critical.join(' | ') || '无';\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 重新计算字符数\n   */\n  recalcChars() {\n    this.totalChars = this.messages.reduce((sum, m) => sum + (m.content?.length || 0), 0);\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 备份历史\n   */\n  async backupHistory() {\n    const backupPath = path.join(this.backupDir, `history_${Date.now()}.json`);\n    try {\n      fs.writeFileSync(backupPath, JSON.stringify(this.messages), 'utf8');\n    } catch (err) {\n      console.warn('[Context] 备份失败:', err.message);\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 回滚\n   */\n  rollback() {\n    try {\n      const files = fs.readdirSync(this.backupDir)\n        .filter(f => f.startsWith('history_') && f.endsWith('.json'))\n        .sort()\n        .reverse();\n      \n      if (files.length === 0) return false;\n      \n      const latestBackup = path.join(this.backupDir, files[0]);\n      this.messages = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(latestBackup, 'utf8'));\n      this.recalcChars();\n      return true;\n    } catch (err) {\n      console.warn('[Context] 回滚失败:', err.message);\n      return false;\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 新消息处理\n   */\n  onNewMessage(message) {\n    this.messages.push({\n      ...message,\n      timestamp: message.timestamp || new Date().toISOString()\n    });\n    this.totalChars += message.content?.length || 0;\n\n    // 检测是否需要压缩\n    const result = this.shouldSummarize();\n    if (result.should) {\n      this.autoSummarize(result.reason);\n    }\n    \n    return result;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 判断是否需要压缩\n   */\n  shouldSummarize() {\n    // 1. 消息条数\n    if (this.messages.length >= this.msgThreshold) {\n      return { should: true, reason: 'message_count' };\n    }\n    \n    // 2. 字符数\n    if (this.totalChars >= this.charThreshold) {\n      return { should: true, reason: 'char_threshold' };\n    }\n    \n    // 3. Token 估算\n    const historyText = this.messages.map(m => m.content || '').join('\\n');\n    const estimatedTokens = this.estimateTokens(historyText);\n    if (estimatedTokens / this.tokenLimit >= this.tokenRatioThreshold) {\n      return { should: true, reason: 'token_estimated' };\n    }\n    \n    // 4. 真实使用率（需底层支持）\n    const real = this.getRealContextUsage();\n    if (real && real.percent >= this.tokenRatioThreshold) {\n      return { should: true, reason: 'token_real' };\n    }\n    \n    return { should: false };\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 定期轮询（每30秒）\n   */\n  startPeriodicCheck() {\n    if (this.checkIntervalMs > 0) {\n      setInterval(() => {\n        const real = this.getRealContextUsage();\n        if (real && real.percent >= this.tokenRatioThreshold) {\n          this.autoSummarize('periodic_poll');\n        }\n      }, this.checkIntervalMs);\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 获取状态\n   */\n  getStatus() {\n    const historyText = this.messages.map(m => m.content || '').join('\\n');\n    const estimatedTokens = this.estimateTokens(historyText);\n    \n    return {\n      messageCount: this.messages.length,\n      totalChars: this.totalChars,\n      estimatedTokens,\n      tokenRatio: (estimatedTokens / this.tokenLimit).toFixed(2),\n      msgThreshold: this.msgThreshold,\n      charThreshold: this.charThreshold,\n      shouldSummarize: this.shouldSummarize(),\n      lastSummarize: this.lastSummarize\n    };\n  }\n}\n\n// 导出单例\nexport const contextProtector = new ContextProtector();\n\nexport default contextProtector;","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/protection/context_protector.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":7101,"output":2015,"cacheRead":114560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123676,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775325569347,"responseId":"019d59a66264023033a44a96daab1cff"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ab94e1c","parentId":"315f1d71","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:01:06.319Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d59a6978bf71cc1d7e4a3e34cf481","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully wrote 6608 bytes to /home/ai/.openclaw/protection/context_protector.js"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775325666314}}
{"type":"message","id":"b5a5b363","parentId":"9ab94e1c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:01:19.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在更新 loader 和 index.js 来包含新的上下文保护模块，并添加熔断器和限流器。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f0f49b6871b84f93ab558ca8","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * OpenCLaw 保护层 - 熔断器与限流\n */\n\nclass CircuitBreaker {\n  constructor(name, options = {}) {\n    this.name = name;\n    this.failureThreshold = options.failureThreshold || 5;\n    this.timeoutSec = options.timeoutSec || 30;\n    this.halfOpenSuccesses = options.halfOpenSuccesses || 3;\n    this.state = 'CLOSED'; // CLOSED, OPEN, HALF_OPEN\n    this.failures = 0;\n    this.lastFailure = 0;\n    this.successesInHalf = 0;\n  }\n\n  async call(fn) {\n    if (this.state === 'OPEN') {\n      if (Date.now() - this.lastFailure < this.timeoutSec * 1000) {\n        throw new Error(`Circuit breaker ${this.name} is OPEN`);\n      }\n      this.state = 'HALF_OPEN';\n      this.successesInHalf = 0;\n    }\n\n    try {\n      const result = await fn();\n      if (this.state === 'HALF_OPEN') {\n        this.successesInHalf++;\n        if (this.successesInHalf >= this.halfOpenSuccesses) {\n          this.state = 'CLOSED';\n          this.failures = 0;\n        }\n      }\n      return result;\n    } catch (err) {\n      this.failures++;\n      this.lastFailure = Date.now();\n      if (this.failures >= this.failureThreshold) {\n        this.state = 'OPEN';\n      }\n      throw err;\n    }\n  }\n\n  getState() {\n    return {\n      name: this.name,\n      state: this.state,\n      failures: this.failures,\n      lastFailure: this.lastFailure\n    };\n  }\n}\n\n/**\n * 令牌桶限流器\n */\nclass RateLimiter {\n  constructor(tokensPerSec = 2, maxTokens = 10) {\n    this.tokens = maxTokens;\n    this.maxTokens = maxTokens;\n    this.rate = tokensPerSec;\n    this.lastRefill = Date.now();\n  }\n\n  acquire() {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    const elapsed = (now - this.lastRefill) / 1000;\n    this.tokens = Math.min(this.maxTokens, this.tokens + elapsed * this.rate);\n    this.lastRefill = now;\n    \n    if (this.tokens >= 1) {\n      this.tokens -= 1;\n      return true;\n    }\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  getStatus() {\n    return {\n      tokens: this.tokens.toFixed(2),\n      maxTokens: this.maxTokens,\n      rate: this.rate\n    };\n  }\n}\n\n// 导出\nexport const circuitBreaker = (name, options) => new CircuitBreaker(name, options);\nexport const rateLimiter = (tokensPerSec, maxTokens) => new RateLimiter(tokensPerSec, maxTokens);\nexport { CircuitBreaker, RateLimiter };\n\nexport default { CircuitBreaker, RateLimiter, circuitBreaker, rateLimiter };","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/protection/circuit_breaker.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":123701,"output":701,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124402,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775325666321,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f9eb1ecb-c1f4-42c1-9eeb-1198b0acb14a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"40a1b375","parentId":"b5a5b363","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:01:19.237Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f0f49b6871b84f93ab558ca8","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully wrote 2281 bytes to /home/ai/.openclaw/protection/circuit_breaker.js"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775325679234}}
{"type":"message","id":"911940de","parentId":"40a1b375","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:01:45.108Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在更新 index.js 来包含所有新模块：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b7e664b7f9804121922e3bad","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * OpenCLaw 保护层 - 主入口 (v4.2)\n * \n * 整合所有保护模块，提供统一的 API\n * \n * 模块：\n * - limiter: 并发限制 + 队列\n * - timeout: 超时 + 无产出检测\n * - truncation: 输出截断存储\n * - memory: 内存限制 + OOM 处理\n * - checkpoint: 检查点 + 恢复\n * - summarize: 会话自动压缩\n * - context_protector: 多维度上下文保护\n * - circuit_breaker: 熔断器与限流\n * \n * 使用方式：\n * import protection from './protection/index.js';\n * \n * // 初始化\n * await protection.init();\n * \n * // 提交任务\n * const taskId = protection.submitTask({ spec: myTask });\n * \n * // 执行带保护的任务\n * await protection.runProtected(taskId, async () => {\n *   // 你的任务逻辑\n * });\n */\n\nimport { taskQueue, limiter } from './limiter.js';\nimport { timeoutController } from './timeout.js';\nimport { outputTruncation } from './truncation.js';\nimport { memoryLimiter } from './memory.js';\nimport { checkpointManager } from './checkpoint.js';\nimport { sessionSummarizer } from './summarize.js';\nimport { contextProtector } from './context_protector.js';\nimport { CircuitBreaker, RateLimiter } from './circuit_breaker.js';\n\nclass ProtectionLayer {\n  constructor() {\n    this.limiter = limiter;\n    this.timeout = timeoutController;\n    this.truncation = outputTruncation;\n    this.memory = memoryLimiter;\n    this.checkpoint = checkpointManager;\n    this.summarizer = sessionSummarizer;\n    this.context = contextProtector;\n    \n    // 熔断器集合\n    this.circuitBreakers = new Map();\n    \n    // 全局限流器\n    this.rateLimiter = new RateLimiter(2, 10);\n    \n    this.initialized = false;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 初始化\n   */\n  async init() {\n    if (this.initialized) return this;\n    \n    console.log('[Protection] 初始化保护层 v4.2...');\n    \n    // 确保输出目录存在\n    const outputDir = process.env.OPENCLAW_OUTPUT_DIR || '/tmp/openclaw';\n    const checkpointDir = process.env.OPENCLAW_CHECKPOINT_DIR || '/tmp/openclaw/checkpoints';\n    \n    try {\n      const fs = await import('fs');\n      [outputDir, checkpointDir].forEach(dir => {\n        if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) {\n          fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true });\n        }\n      });\n    } catch (err) {\n      console.warn('[Protection] 目录创建失败:', err.message);\n    }\n    \n    this.initialized = true;\n    console.log('[Protection] 保护层初始化完成');\n    \n    return this;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 提交受保护的任务\n   */\n  submitTask(taskSpec) {\n    // 检查限流\n    if (!this.rateLimiter.acquire()) {\n      const err = new Error('RATE_LIMITED');\n      err.code = 429;\n      throw err;\n    }\n    \n    return this.limiter.submit({\n      id: taskSpec.id,\n      spec: taskSpec,\n      priority: taskSpec.priority || 0\n    });\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 运行受保护的任务\n   */\n  async runProtected(taskId, taskFn, options = {}) {\n    const {\n      timeoutMs = 60000,\n      enableCheckpoint = false,\n      enableMemoryLimit = true,\n      enableOutputTruncation = true,\n      stepExtractor = null\n    } = options;\n\n    // 启动超时监控\n    this.timeout.startTask(taskId, timeoutMs, options);\n\n    try {\n      let result;\n\n      if (enableCheckpoint && stepExtractor) {\n        result = await this.checkpoint.resume(\n          { id: taskId, steps: stepExtractor() },\n          async (task, startStep) => {\n            const steps = task.steps;\n            for (let i = startStep; i < steps.length; i++) {\n              await taskFn(steps[i], i);\n              this.checkpoint.saveCheckpoint(taskId, {\n                status: 'running',\n                lastCompletedStep: i,\n                totalSteps: steps.length\n              });\n            }\n            return { completed: true, stepsCompleted: steps.length };\n          }\n        );\n      } else {\n        result = await taskFn();\n      }\n\n      this.timeout.complete(taskId);\n      this.limiter.complete(taskId);\n      \n      if (enableCheckpoint) {\n        this.checkpoint.deleteCheckpoint(taskId);\n      }\n\n      return result;\n\n    } catch (error) {\n      this.limiter.fail(taskId, error);\n      throw error;\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * Spawn 带保护的子代理\n   */\n  async spawnSubagent(config) {\n    const {\n      task,\n      runtime = 'subagent',\n      timeoutSeconds = 300,\n      enableMemoryLimit = true\n    } = config;\n\n    const taskId = `subagent_${Date.now()}_${Math.random().toString(36).substr(2, 9)}`;\n\n    const queuedTaskId = this.limiter.submit({\n      id: taskId,\n      spec: config\n    });\n\n    return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n      this.timeout.startTask(taskId, timeoutSeconds * 1000);\n\n      setImmediate(async () => {\n        try {\n          // TODO: 实际调用 spawn\n          // const spawnFn = global.openclaw_spawn || (() => { throw new Error('not configured'); });\n          // const result = await spawnFn({ task, runtime, timeoutSeconds });\n          \n          // 模拟\n          const result = { taskId, status: 'simulated' };\n          \n          this.timeout.complete(taskId);\n          this.limiter.complete(taskId);\n          resolve(result);\n\n        } catch (error) {\n          this.limiter.fail(taskId, error);\n          reject(error);\n        }\n      });\n    });\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 获取或创建熔断器\n   */\n  getCircuitBreaker(name, options) {\n    if (!this.circuitBreakers.has(name)) {\n      this.circuitBreakers.set(name, new CircuitBreaker(name, options));\n    }\n    return this.circuitBreakers.get(name);\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 处理新消息（触发上下文保护）\n   */\n  handleMessage(message) {\n    // 更新会话历史\n    this.summarizer.addMessage(message);\n    \n    // 触发多维度检测\n    const result = this.context.onNewMessage(message);\n    \n    return result;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 获取所有模块状态\n   */\n  getStatus() {\n    return {\n      limiter: this.limiter.getStatus(),\n      timeout: this.timeout.getStatus(),\n      truncation: this.truncation.getStatus(),\n      memory: this.memory.getStatus(),\n      summarizer: this.summarizer.getStatus(),\n      context: this.context.getStatus(),\n      rateLimiter: this.rateLimiter.getStatus(),\n      circuitBreakers: Array.from(this.circuitBreakers.values()).map(cb => cb.getState())\n    };\n  }\n}\n\n// 创建单例\nconst protection = new ProtectionLayer();\n\nexport default protection;\nexport { protection };\n\n// 自动初始化（如果已启用）\nif (typeof process !== 'undefined' && process.env?.OPENCLAW_PROTECTION_ENABLED === 'true') {\n  protection.init().catch(console.error);\n}","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/protection/index.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":124441,"output":1633,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126074,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775325679239,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c3c7713d-52e3-4050-a6a2-9c651ae65dca"}}
