{"type":"message","id":"132b7b80","parentId":"dd1c62d9","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:09:09.862Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"修复完成，让我给用户一个总结。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 漏洞修复完成\n\n### 已修复\n\n| 漏洞 | 文件 | 修复内容 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **并发竞态** | limiter.js | 添加 `_lock` 简单锁 |\n| **路径遍历** | checkpoint.js | 添加 `validateTaskId()` + 路径验证 |\n| **定时器泄漏** | context_protector.js | 保存 interval ID + `destroy()` |\n\n### 验证结果\n\n```\n✅ 正常ID: true\n✅ 路径遍历已阻止: true\n✅ limiter 仍然工作\n✅ 语法检查通过\n```\n\n### 剩余（低危）\n\n- 缺少结构化日志\n- 缺少健康检查接口\n\n**要我继续修复剩余问题吗？** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":138709,"output":165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138874,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775326146292,"responseId":"chatcmpl-229bda61-2f6a-4a25-8061-59ef1a903011"}}
