{"type":"message","id":"fbd56c73","parentId":"fdf68d8c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:14:25.684Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要详细介绍一下保护层 v4.2，让我给出一个全面的介绍。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 🛡️ OpenClaw 保护层 v4.2 - 详细介绍\n\n---\n\n### 一、为什么需要保护层？\n\n解决任务执行中的各种\"卡死\"问题：\n\n| 问题 | 后果 | 保护方案 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 任务卡死 | 无限等待 | 超时强制终止 |\n| 输出刷屏 | 上下文爆炸 | 截断存文件 |\n| 内存溢出 | OOM被杀 | setrlimit限制 |\n| 上下文超限 | 会话崩溃 | 多维度自动压缩 |\n| 并发过高 | 资源耗尽 | 全局队列限制 |\n| 任务中断 | 进度丢失 | 检查点恢复 |\n| 外部API失败 | 连锁反应 | 熔断器保护 |\n| 主循环卡死 | 系统崩溃 | 健康监控+自愈 |\n\n---\n\n### 二、完整模块介绍\n\n#### 1. limiter.js - 并发限制与队列\n```\n功能：最多3个任务并行，超出自动排队\n状态：✅ 已修复并发竞态\n```\n\n```javascript\n// 使用\nprotection.submitTask({ spec: myTask })\n// 返回 taskId，自动排队调度\n```\n\n#### 2. timeout.js - 超时与无产出检测\n```\n功能：任务超时 + 30秒无产出判定卡死\n       SIGTERM → 等待5秒 → SIGKILL\n```\n\n#### 3. truncation.js - 输出截断存储\n```\n功能：输出>10KB自动截断，存到/tmp/openclaw/\n       终端只显示最后1KB\n       24小时后自动清理\n```\n\n#### 4. memory.js - 内存限制与OOM处理\n```\n功能：setrlimit限制2GB内存\n       OOM自动重试（1s,2s,4s指数退避）\n       连续3次OOM冻结任务\n```\n\n#### 5. checkpoint.js - 检查点与恢复\n```\n功能：每步完成后原子写入检查点\n       SHA256校验和验证完整性\n       启动时自动恢复未完成任务\n状态：✅ 已修复路径遍历漏洞\n```\n\n#### 6. summarize.js - 会话自动压缩\n```\n功能：消息≥50条自动压缩\n       保留摘要+最近5条消息\n       支持回滚\n```\n\n#### 7. context_protector.js - 多维度上下文保护\n```\n功能：检测三个维度\n       - 消息条数 ≥50\n       - 字符数 ≥100KB\n       - Token估算 ≥80%\n状态：✅ 已修复定时器泄漏\n```\n\n#### 8. circuit_breaker.js - 熔断器与限流\n```\n功能：外部API连续失败5次→熔断30秒\n       令牌桶限流（2次/秒）\n```\n\n#### 9. logger.js - 结构化日志 ✨新增\n```\n功能：JSON Lines格式\n       每秒限速100条\n       自动轮转（100MB/文件）\n```\n\n#### 10. health_checker.js - 健康检查 ✨新增\n```\n功能：每10秒健康检查\n       主循环心跳监控\n       资源使用告警\n       自愈建议\n```\n\n---\n\n### 三、执行流程\n\n```\n收到任务\n    ↓\n【评分】task-weight-estimator (0-6分)\n    ↓\n【路由】\n  0-1分 → 直接执行 (30秒超时)\n  2-3分 → 拆步骤存档 (60秒/步)\n  4-5分 → spawn子代理 (max(60,总分×60)秒)\n  6分   → 多子代理并行\n    ↓\n【保护执行】\n  ├─ 并发限制（最多3个）\n  ├─ 超时监控\n  ├─ 无产出检测\n  ├─ 输出截断\n  ├─ 内存限制\n  ├─ 检查点存档\n  └─ 上下文监控\n    ↓\n【日志】JSON Lines → /tmp/openclaw/logs/\n    ↓\n【健康检查】每10秒一次\n    ↓\n【完成/失败/冻结】\n```\n\n---\n\n### 四、配置参数\n\n| 环境变量 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|----------|--------|------|\n| MAX_CONCURRENT | 3 | 最大并发 |\n| DIRECT_TIMEOUT | 30000ms | 直接执行超时 |\n| MAX_OUTPUT_KB | 10 | 输出截断阈值 |\n| MEMORY_SOFT_MB | 2000 | 内存软限制 |\n| MSG_THRESHOLD | 50 | 消息压缩阈值 |\n| CHAR_THRESHOLD | 102400 | 字符压缩阈值 |\n| TOKEN_RATIO | 0.8 | Token使用率阈值 |\n\n---\n\n### 五、使用示例\n\n```javascript\nimport protection from './protection/index.js';\n\n// 初始化\nawait protection.init();\n\n// 提交任务（自动并发限制）\nconst taskId = protection.submitTask({ \n  spec: { cmd: 'my_command' }\n});\n\n// 执行带保护\nconst result = await protection.runProtected(taskId, async () => {\n  // 任务逻辑\n  return { success: true };\n}, { timeoutMs: 60000 });\n\n// 查询状态\nconsole.log(protection.getStatus());\n\n// 健康检查\nconsole.log(protection.health.getHealth());\n```\n\n---\n\n### 六、状态查询\n\n```bash\n# 查看所有模块状态\nprotection.getStatus()\n\n# 健康检查\nprotection.health.getHealth()\n# 返回: { healthy: true/false, issues: [...] }\n```\n\n---\n\n**保护层 v4.2 - 让任务执行永远不卡死！** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":145003,"output":1173,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146176,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775326447014,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e1158bb5-1e53-4da2-86a6-9565a4a81477"}}
{"type":"message","id":"65b279f4","parentId":"fbd56c73","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:38:17.820Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 02:38 GMT+8] 学习：# OpenClaw 最优解 v4.3：全自动高鲁棒安全高效执行系统\n\n> 本版本整合了任务确保执行、防卡死、上下文保护、安全性、效率优化，经过多轮自我审查修正，**已达到当前认知下的最优**。 \n> 核心原则：**永不卡死、永不丢失、永不泄露、高效可控**。\n\n---\n\n## 一、总体架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 用户接口层 │\n│ CLI / HTTP / 消息队列 │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n │\n ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 安全网关层 │\n│ - 限流（令牌桶，每IP每秒2次） │\n│ - 命令白名单（仅允许 /usr/bin/ 下的程序） │\n│ - 路径沙箱（禁止 ../ 和绝对路径，除非在 /tmp/openclaw/inputs/） │\n│ - 任务规格大小限制（≤1MB） │\n│ - 敏感信息脱敏（password/token 替换为 ***） │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n │\n ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 持久化队列层（SQLite WAL） │\n│ - 任务表：id, spec, status, retries, lease_expiry, checkpoint │\n│ - 事件表：审计日志、任务事件 │\n│ - 索引：status+priority+created_at 复合索引 │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n │\n ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 调度器（自适应轮询） │\n│ - 并发控制（默认3，可动态调整） │\n│ - 优先级队列（priority 0-10，数字越大越优先） │\n│ - 租约恢复（每60秒清理过期 RUNNING 任务） │\n│ - 空闲退避（无任务时轮询间隔从10ms→1000ms） │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n │\n ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 任务执行沙箱（子进程） │\n│ - 超时 & 无产出检测（全局硬超时 + 步骤级超时） │\n│ - 输出截断缓冲（64KB批量写入，结束时 flush） │\n│ - 内存限制（通过 `ulimit` 或 `prlimit`） │\n│ - 权限降级（uid/gid=nobody） │\n│ - 检查点（长任务，支持延迟写入，可配置立即 fsync） │\n│ - 幂等性支持（idempotency key 检查） │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n │\n ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 上下文保护 & 长期记忆 │\n│ - 多维度触发（消息数≥50 或 字符数≥100KB 或 token≥80%） │\n│ - 增量 token 计数（维护滑动窗口，压缩时重新计算） │\n│ - 摘要写入记忆（支持回滚） │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n │\n ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 可观测性 & 自愈 │\n│ - 结构化日志（pino 异步，每秒限速200条） │\n│ - 健康检查（每30秒，连续3次失败才 abort） │\n│ - 磁盘空间监控（<5% 暂停新任务，自动清理旧临时文件） │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 二、模块伪代码（已修正并优化）\n\n### 2.1 安全网关\n\n```javascript\n// security_gate.js\nconst fs = require('fs').promises;\nconst path = require('path');\n\nclass SecurityGate {\n constructor(config) {\n this.allowedCommands = config.allowedCommands || ['/usr/bin/ls', '/usr/bin/cat', '/usr/bin/grep', '/usr/bin/python3'];\n this.maxSpecSize = config.maxSpecSize || 1024 * 1024;\n this.rateLimitPerSec = config.rateLimitPerSec || 2;\n // 令牌桶 per IP\n this.tokens = new Map(); // ip -> { tokens, lastRefill }\n }\n\n // 限流检查\n rateLimit(ip) {\n const now = Date.now();\n let entry = this.tokens.get(ip);\n if (!entry) {\n entry = { tokens: this.rateLimitPerSec, lastRefill: now };\n this.tokens.set(ip, entry);\n }\n const elapsed = (now - entry.lastRefill) / 1000;\n entry.tokens = Math.min(this.rateLimitPerSec, entry.tokens + elapsed * this.rateLimitPerSec);\n entry.lastRefill = now;\n if (entry.tokens >= 1) {\n entry.tokens -= 1;\n return true;\n }\n throw new Error('Rate limit exceeded');\n }\n\n // 命令白名单 + 路径沙箱\n async validateCommand(cmd, args) {\n // 1. 解析绝对路径\n let resolved;\n try {\n resolved = await fs.realpath(cmd);\n } catch {\n throw new Error(`Command not found: ${cmd}`);\n }\n if (!this.allowedCommands.includes(resolved)) {\n throw new Error(`Command ${cmd} not allowed`);\n }\n // 2. 检查参数中的路径遍历\n for (const arg of args) {\n if (arg.includes('..') || (arg.startsWith('/') && !arg.startsWith('/tmp/openclaw/inputs/'))) {\n throw new Error(`Argument ${arg} contains forbidden path`);\n }\n }\n return true;\n }\n\n // 规格大小限制\n validateSpecSize(spec) {\n const size = JSON.stringify(spec).length;\n if (size > this.maxSpecSize) throw new Error(`Spec size ${size} exceeds limit ${this.maxSpecSize}`);\n }\n\n // 敏感信息脱敏（用于日志）\n sanitizeSpec(spec) {\n const sensitive = ['password', 'token', 'secret', 'api_key'];\n let str = JSON.stringify(spec);\n for (const s of sensitive) {\n const re = new RegExp(`\"(${s})\"\\\\s*:\\\\s*\"[^\"]*\"`, 'gi');\n str = str.replace(re, `\"$1\":\"***\"`);\n }\n return JSON.parse(str);\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 持久化队列（批量提交优化）\n\n```javascript\n// task_queue.js\nconst sqlite3 = require('sqlite3').verbose();\nconst db = new sqlite3.Database('/var/openclaw/tasks.db');\ndb.run('PRAGMA journal_mode=WAL');\ndb.run('PRAGMA synchronous=NORMAL'); // 平衡性能与安全\ndb.run(`CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS tasks (\n id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n spec TEXT,\n status TEXT,\n retries INTEGER,\n max_retries INTEGER,\n worker_id TEXT,\n lease_expiry INTEGER,\n checkpoint TEXT,\n created_at INTEGER,\n started_at INTEGER,\n finished_at INTEGER,\n last_error TEXT,\n next_retry_at INTEGER,\n idempotent INTEGER,\n priority INTEGER DEFAULT 0\n)`);\ndb.run(`CREATE INDEX idx_status_priority ON tasks(status, priority DESC, created_at)`);\n\nclass PersistentQueue {\n constructor() {\n this.pendingWrites = []; // 批量写入队列\n this.flushTimer = null;\n }\n\n // 批量提交（每10ms或积攒20条）\n enqueue(sql, params) {\n this.pendingWrites.push({ sql, params });\n if (!this.flushTimer) {\n this.flushTimer = setTimeout(() => this.flush(), 10);\n }\n if (this.pendingWrites.length >= 20) this.flush();\n }\n\n async flush() {\n if (!this.pendingWrites.length) return;\n const batch = this.pendingWrites;\n this.pendingWrites = [];\n this.flushTimer = null;\n await db.exec('BEGIN');\n try {\n for (const { sql, params } of batch) {\n await db.run(sql, params);\n }\n await db.exec('COMMIT');\n } catch (err) {\n await db.exec('ROLLBACK');\n throw err;\n }\n }\n\n async submit(taskSpec, userId, ip) {\n const taskId = require('crypto').randomUUID();\n const idempotent = taskSpec.idempotent === true ? 1 : 0;\n const priority = taskSpec.priority || 0;\n const sql = `INSERT INTO tasks (id, spec, status, retries, max_retries, created_at, idempotent, priority)\n VALUES (?, ?, 'PENDING', 0, ?, ?, ?, ?)`;\n this.enqueue(sql, [taskId, JSON.stringify(taskSpec), taskSpec.maxRetries || 3, Date.now(), idempotent, priority]);\n await this.logAudit(taskId, userId, 'SUBMIT', JSON.stringify({ ip }), ip);\n return taskId;\n }\n\n async claimTask(workerId, leaseSec = 60) {\n const now = Date.now();\n const expiry = now + leaseSec * 1000;\n // 原子更新：只取一个PENDING任务，按优先级和创建时间排序\n const res = await db.run(`\n UPDATE tasks \n SET status = 'RUNNING', worker_id = ?, lease_expiry = ?, started_at = ?\n WHERE status = 'PENDING' AND (next_retry_at IS NULL OR next_retry_at <= ?)\n ORDER BY priority DESC, created_at ASC\n LIMIT 1\n `, workerId, expiry, now, now);\n if (res.changes === 0) return null;\n const row = await db.get(`SELECT * FROM tasks WHERE worker_id = ?`, workerId);\n if (row) row.spec = JSON.parse(row.spec);\n return row;\n }\n\n async completeTask(taskId, success, errorMsg = null) {\n const status = success ? 'SUCCESS' : 'FAILED';\n this.enqueue(`UPDATE tasks SET status = ?, finished_at = ?, last_error = ? WHERE id = ?`,\n [status, Date.now(), errorMsg, taskId]);\n }\n\n async markDeadLetter(taskId, errorMsg) {\n this.enqueue(`UPDATE tasks SET status = 'DEAD_LETTER', last_error = ?, finished_at = ? WHERE id = ?`,\n [errorMsg, Date.now(), taskId]);\n }\n\n async recoverStaleTasks(now) {\n await db.run(`\n UPDATE tasks \n SET status = 'PENDING', worker_id = NULL, lease_expiry = NULL\n WHERE status = 'RUNNING' AND lease_expiry < ?\n `, now);\n }\n\n async logEvent(taskId, event, meta) {\n this.enqueue(`INSERT INTO task_events (task_id, event, meta, created_at) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)`,\n [taskId, event, JSON.stringify(meta), Date.now()]);\n }\n\n async logAudit(taskId, userId, action, detail, ip) {\n this.enqueue(`INSERT INTO audit_log (task_id, user_id, action, detail, ip, created_at) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)`,\n [taskId, userId, action, detail, ip, Date.now()]);\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.3 调度器（自适应轮询）\n\n```javascript\n// scheduler.js\nclass AdaptiveScheduler {\n constructor(queue, maxConcurrent = 3) {\n this.queue = queue;\n this.maxConcurrent = maxConcurrent;\n this.active = 0;\n this.workerId = `${process.pid}_${Date.now()}`;\n this.pollInterval = 10; // 初始10ms\n this.idleCount = 0;\n this.running = true;\n // 租约续期（每30秒）\n setInterval(() => this.renewLeases(), 30000);\n // 恢复过期任务（每60秒）\n setInterval(() => this.recoverStale(), 60000);\n this.loop();\n }\n\n async renewLeases() {\n const now = Date.now();\n const newExpiry = now + 60000;\n await db.run(`UPDATE tasks SET lease_expiry = ? WHERE worker_id = ? AND status = 'RUNNING'`,\n [newExpiry, this.workerId]);\n }\n\n async recoverStale() {\n await this.queue.recoverStaleTasks(Date.now());\n }\n\n async loop() {\n while (this.running) {\n if (this.active >= this.maxConcurrent) {\n await this.sleep(100);\n continue;\n }\n const task = await this.queue.claimTask(this.workerId);\n if (!task) {\n // 空闲退避：逐渐增加轮询间隔，最大1秒\n this.idleCount++;\n let interval = Math.min(1000, 10 * Math.pow(1.5, this.idleCount));\n await this.sleep(interval);\n continue;\n }\n this.idleCount = 0;\n this.active++;\n this.executeTask(task).finally(() => {\n this.active--;\n });\n }\n }\n\n async executeTask(task) {\n const executor = new TaskExecutor(task, this.queue);\n try {\n await executor.run();\n await this.queue.completeTask(task.id, true);\n } catch (err) {\n await this.handleFailure(task, err);\n }\n }\n\n async handleFailure(task, error) {\n const isRetryable = error.isRetryable || error.code === 'ETIMEDOUT' || error.message.includes('OOM');\n const newRetries = task.retries + 1;\n if (isRetryable && newRetries <= task.max_retries && task.idempotent) {\n const delay = Math.min(300000, Math.pow(2, newRetries) * 1000);\n await db.run(`\n UPDATE tasks \n SET status = 'PENDING', retries = ?, next_retry_at = ?, last_error = ?, \n worker_id = NULL, lease_expiry = NULL\n WHERE id = ?\n `, newRetries, Date.now() + delay, error.message, task.id);\n await this.queue.logEvent(task.id, 'RETRY', { attempt: newRetries, delay });\n } else {\n await this.queue.markDeadLetter(task.id, error.message);\n }\n }\n\n sleep(ms) { return new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, ms)); }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.4 任务执行沙箱（关键修正点）\n\n```javascript\n// task_executor.js\nconst { spawn } = require('child_process');\nconst fs = require('fs').promises;\nconst path = require('path');\n\nclass TaskExecutor {\n constructor(task, queue) {\n this.task = task;\n this.queue = queue;\n this.timeoutMs = task.spec.timeout || 600000;\n this.memoryLimitMB = task.spec.memoryLimit || 2048;\n this.truncator = null;\n this.proc = null;\n }\n\n async run() {\n const gate = new SecurityGate({});\n await gate.validateCommand(this.task.spec.cmd, this.task.spec.args || []);\n \n const tempDir = `/tmp/openclaw/task_${this.task.id}`;\n await fs.mkdir(tempDir, { recursive: true, mode: 0o700 });\n\n // 使用 ulimit 包装命令来实现内存限制（兼容性好）\n const cmd = this.task.spec.cmd;\n const args = this.task.spec.args || [];\n const limitCmd = `ulimit -v ${this.memoryLimitMB * 1024} && exec \"$@\"`;\n const shellArgs = ['-c', limitCmd, '--', cmd, ...args];\n\n this.proc = spawn('/bin/sh', shellArgs, {\n cwd: tempDir,\n env: { ...process.env, TASK_ID: this.task.id, ...(this.task.spec.env || {}) },\n uid: 65534,\n gid: 65534,\n stdio: ['ignore', 'pipe', 'pipe']\n });\n\n this.truncator = new BufferedOutputTruncator(this.task.id, 10 * 1024);\n this.proc.stdout.on('data', data => this.truncator.write(data));\n this.proc.stderr.on('data', data => this.truncator.write(data));\n\n // 超时与无产出检测\n let lastOutput = Date.now();\n const outputInterval = setInterval(() => {\n if (Date.now() - lastOutput > 30000 && this.proc && !this.proc.killed) {\n this.proc.kill('SIGUSR1');\n setTimeout(() => {\n if (Date.now() - lastOutput > 60000 && this.proc && !this.proc.killed) {\n this.proc.kill('SIGKILL');\n }\n }, 30000);\n }\n }, 10000);\n this.proc.stdout.on('data', () => { lastOutput = Date.now(); });\n this.proc.stderr.on('data', () => { lastOutput = Date.now(); });\n\n const timeoutId = setTimeout(() => {\n if (this.proc && !this.proc.killed) {\n this.proc.kill('SIGTERM');\n setTimeout(() => {\n if (this.proc && !this.proc.killed) this.proc.kill('SIGKILL');\n }, 5000);\n }\n }, this.timeoutMs);\n\n const code = await new Promise((resolve) => {\n this.proc.on('close', resolve);\n });\n clearTimeout(timeoutId);\n clearInterval(outputInterval);\n await this.truncator.close();\n\n if (code !== 0) {\n const error = new Error(`Process exited with code ${code}`);\n error.isRetryable = (code === 137); // SIGKILL → OOM\n throw error;\n }\n\n // 清理临时目录\n await fs.rm(tempDir, { recursive: true, force: true });\n }\n}\n\n// 输出截断：缓冲批量写入 + 结束时 flush\nclass BufferedOutputTruncator {\n constructor(taskId, maxBytes) {\n this.taskId = taskId;\n this.maxBytes = maxBytes;\n this.buffer = '';\n this.total = 0;\n this.tempFile = null;\n this.overflow = false;\n this.flushTimer = null;\n }\n\n async write(data) {\n const str = data.toString();\n this.total += str.length;\n if (!this.overflow && this.total <= this.maxBytes) {\n this.buffer += str;\n process.stdout.write(str);\n if (this.buffer.length > 64 * 1024) await this.flush();\n return;\n }\n if (!this.overflow) {\n this.overflow = true;\n const dir = '/tmp/openclaw/outputs';\n await fs.mkdir(dir, { recursive: true });\n this.tempFile = await fs.open(path.join(dir, `task_${this.taskId}.out`), 'w');\n // 写入之前缓冲的最后1KB\n const tail = this.buffer.slice(-1024);\n await this.tempFile.write(this.buffer);\n this.buffer = tail;\n console.log(`[Output truncated] Full log: /tmp/openclaw/outputs/task_${this.taskId}.out`);\n }\n if (this.tempFile) {\n this.buffer += str;\n if (this.buffer.length > 64 * 1024) await this.flush();\n if (!this.flushTimer) {\n this.flushTimer = setTimeout(() => this.flush(), 1000);\n }\n }\n }\n\n async flush() {\n if (this.flushTimer) clearTimeout(this.flushTimer);\n this.flushTimer = null;\n if (this.buffer && this.tempFile) {\n await this.tempFile.write(this.buffer);\n this.buffer = '';\n }\n }\n\n async close() {\n await this.flush();\n if (this.tempFile) {\n await this.tempFile.close();\n console.log(`Full output saved to /tmp/openclaw/outputs/task_${this.taskId}.out`);\n // 显示最后1KB\n console.log('Last 1KB:\\n' + this.buffer.slice(-1024));\n }\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.5 检查点（支持延迟/立即刷盘）\n\n```javascript\n// checkpoint.js\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst fs = require('fs').promises;\nconst path = require('path');\n\nclass CheckpointManager {\n constructor(taskId, immediate = false) {\n this.taskId = taskId;\n this.immediate = immediate; // 关键任务立即 fsync\n this.dir = '/var/openclaw/checkpoints';\n this.latest = null;\n this.pendingFlush = null;\n }\n\n async save(stepIndex, data) {\n const payload = { taskId: this.taskId, stepIndex, data, timestamp: Date.now(), version: 2 };\n const signature = crypto.createHmac('sha256', process.env.CHECKPOINT_SECRET || 'default')\n .update(JSON.stringify(payload)).digest('hex');\n this.latest = { payload, signature };\n if (this.immediate) {\n await this._writeNow();\n } else {\n if (!this.pendingFlush) {\n this.pendingFlush = setTimeout(() => this._writeNow(), 5000);\n }\n }\n }\n\n async _writeNow() {\n if (this.pendingFlush) clearTimeout(this.pendingFlush);\n this.pendingFlush = null;\n if (!this.latest) return;\n const tmp = path.join(this.dir, `${this.taskId}.tmp`);\n const final = path.join(this.dir, `${this.taskId}.json`);\n await fs.mkdir(this.dir, { recursive: true, mode: 0o700 });\n await fs.writeFile(tmp, JSON.stringify(this.latest));\n if (this.immediate) await fs.fsync(tmp);\n await fs.rename(tmp, final);\n await fs.copyFile(final, final + '.bak');\n }\n\n async load() {\n const file = path.join(this.dir, `${this.taskId}.json`);\n try {\n const content = await fs.readFile(file, 'utf8');\n const cp = JSON.parse(content);\n const expected = crypto.createHmac('sha256', process.env.CHECKPOINT_SECRET || 'default')\n .update(JSON.stringify(cp.payload)).digest('hex');\n if (cp.signature !== expected) throw new Error('Invalid signature');\n return cp.payload;\n } catch (e) {\n const backup = file + '.bak';\n if (await fs.exists(backup)) {\n const content = await fs.readFile(backup, 'utf8');\n return JSON.parse(content).payload;\n }\n return null;\n }\n }\n\n async clear() {\n await this._writeNow(); // 最后一次刷盘\n await fs.unlink(path.join(this.dir, `${this.taskId}.json`)).catch(() => {});\n await fs.unlink(path.join(this.dir, `${this.taskId}.json.bak`)).catch(() => {});\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.6 上下文保护（增量 token 计数 + 滑动窗口）\n\n```javascript\n// context_protector.js\nclass ContextProtector {\n constructor(memoryStore) {\n this.messages = [];\n this.totalTokens = 0;\n this.tokenWindow = []; // 存储每条消息的 token 数，用于压缩时扣除\n this.lastSummarize = 0;\n this.memory = memoryStore;\n this.threshold = { msgs: 50, chars: 100 * 1024, tokenRatio: 0.8, tokenLimit: 128 * 1024, cooldownSec: 120 };\n }\n\n // 轻量 token 估算（缓存）\n countTokens(text) {\n // 使用 tiktoken 或近似：英文 4 字符/token，中文 1.5 字符/token\n const ch = (text.match(/[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]/g) || []).length;\n const other = text.length - ch;\n return Math.ceil(ch / 1.5 + other / 4);\n }\n\n async addMessage(role, content, taskId = null) {\n const tokens = this.countTokens(content);\n this.messages.push({ role, content, timestamp: Date.now(), taskId, tokens });\n this.totalTokens += tokens;\n this.tokenWindow.push(tokens);\n if (this.shouldSummarize()) {\n await this.summarize();\n }\n }\n\n shouldSummarize() {\n if (this.messages.length >= this.threshold.msgs) return true;\n const totalChars = this.messages.reduce((s, m) => s + m.content.length, 0);\n if (totalChars >= this.threshold.chars) return true;\n if (this.totalTokens / this.threshold.tokenLimit >= this.threshold.tokenRatio) return true;\n return false;\n }\n\n async summarize() {\n if (Date.now() - this.lastSummarize < this.threshold.cooldownSec * 1000) return;\n const toSummarize = this.messages.slice(0, -10);\n let summary;\n try {\n summary = await this.callSummarizeAPI(toSummarize.map(m => m.content).join('\\n'));\n } catch (e) {\n summary = `[Fallback] ${toSummarize.length} messages, key info: ${this.extractKeyInfo(toSummarize)}`;\n }\n // 写入长期记忆\n const memoryId = await this.memory.add({\n type: 'conversation_summary',\n content: summary,\n relatedTasks: [...new Set(toSummarize.map(m => m.taskId).filter(Boolean))],\n timestamp: Date.now()\n });\n // 保留最近10条消息\n const kept = this.messages.slice(-10);\n // 重新计算 totalTokens（增量维护复杂，直接重算）\n this.totalTokens = kept.reduce((sum, m) => sum + m.tokens, 0);\n this.messages = [\n { role: 'system', content: `[摘要已存储，ID: ${memoryId}]`, tokens: this.countTokens(`[摘要已存储，ID: ${memoryId}]`) },\n ...kept\n ];\n this.totalTokens += this.messages[0].tokens;\n this.lastSummarize = Date.now();\n }\n\n extractKeyInfo(messages) {\n const text = messages.map(m => m.content).join('\\n');\n const ids = text.match(/task_[a-f0-9-]+/gi) || [];\n const errors = text.match(/error|fail|exception/gi) || [];\n return `任务ID: ${ids.join(',')}, 错误: ${errors.join(',')}`;\n }\n\n async callSummarizeAPI(text) {\n const controller = new AbortController();\n const timeout = setTimeout(() => controller.abort(), 30000);\n const response = await fetch('https://api.summarizer/v1/summarize', {\n method: 'POST',\n headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n body: JSON.stringify({ text, max_tokens: 500 }),\n signal: controller.signal\n });\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n const data = await response.json();\n return data.summary;\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.7 健康检查与磁盘监控\n\n```javascript\n// health.js\nlet lastLoopTime = Date.now();\nlet consecutiveFailures = 0;\n\nfunction updateHeartbeat() { lastLoopTime = Date.now(); }\n\nsetInterval(() => {\n const now = Date.now();\n if (now - lastLoopTime > 15000) {\n consecutiveFailures++;\n console.error(`Main loop unresponsive for ${now - lastLoopTime}ms, failures=${consecutiveFailures}`);\n if (consecutiveFailures >= 3) {\n console.error('Aborting for systemd restart');\n process.exit(1); // 触发 systemd 重启\n }\n } else {\n consecutiveFailures = 0;\n }\n}, 10000);\n\n// 磁盘空间监控\nasync function checkDiskSpace() {\n const { free } = await fs.statfs('/tmp');\n if (free < 100 * 1024 * 1024) {\n console.error('Low disk space, pausing new tasks');\n global.pauseNewTasks = true;\n await cleanupOldFiles('/tmp/openclaw/outputs', 6, 512);\n await cleanupOldFiles('/tmp/openclaw/logs', 24, 1024);\n const { free: newFree } = await fs.statfs('/tmp');\n if (newFree > 200 * 1024 * 1024) global.pauseNewTasks = false;\n }\n}\nsetInterval(checkDiskSpace, 300000);\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、配置与环境变量（默认值）\n\n```bash\n# 数据库\nDATABASE_URL=sqlite:/var/openclaw/tasks.db?journal_mode=WAL\n\n# 调度\nMAX_CONCURRENT=3\nSCHEDULER_POLL_MIN_MS=10\nSCHEDULER_POLL_MAX_MS=1000\n\n# 任务执行\nTASK_GLOBAL_TIMEOUT_MS=600000\nTASK_MEMORY_LIMIT_MB=2048\nMAX_RETRIES=3\nRETRY_BASE_DELAY_MS=1000\n\n# 输出截断\nMAX_OUTPUT_KB=10\nOUTPUT_BUFFER_KB=64\nOUTPUT_TEMP_RETENTION_HOURS=24\nMAX_TEMP_DIR_SIZE_MB=1024\n\n# 检查点\nCHECKPOINT_IMMEDIATE=false # 关键任务设为 true\nCHECKPOINT_SECRET=auto-generated\n\n# 上下文保护\nMSG_SUMMARIZE_THRESHOLD=50\nCHAR_SUMMARIZE_THRESHOLD=102400\nTOKEN_LIMIT=131072\nTOKEN_USAGE_RATIO=0.8\nSUMMARIZE_COOLDOWN_SEC=120\n\n# 安全\nALLOWED_COMMANDS=/usr/bin/ls,/usr/bin/cat,/usr/bin/grep,/usr/bin/python3\nTASK_UID=65534\nTASK_GID=65534\nRATE_LIMIT_PER_SEC=2\nMAX_SPEC_SIZE_BYTES=1048576\n\n# 日志\nLOG_LEVEL=info\nLOG_MAX_SIZE_MB=100\nLOG_MAX_FILES=10\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、部署与测试清单\n\n### 4.1 初始化步骤\n\n```bash\n# 1. 创建目录\nmkdir -p /var/openclaw/{checkpoints,logs} /tmp/openclaw/{inputs,outputs}\nchown -R openclaw:openclaw /var/openclaw /tmp/openclaw\n\n# 2. 初始化数据库（运行一次）\nnode scripts/init_db.js\n\n# 3. 生成检查点密钥（写入 .env）\necho \"CHECKPOINT_SECRET=$(openssl rand -hex 32)\" >> .env\n\n# 4. 配置 systemd 服务\ncat > /etc/systemd/system/openclaw.service <<EOF\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Executor\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nUser=openclaw\nWorkingDirectory=/opt/openclaw\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node scheduler.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=10\nLimitNOFILE=65536\nMemoryMax=4G\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\nEOF\nsystemctl enable openclaw\nsystemctl start openclaw\n```\n\n### 4.2 测试场景\n\n- [ ] 正常任务：`echo hello` → 成功，输出显示\n- [ ] 超时任务：`sleep 600` → 被全局超时杀死，返回 TIMEOUT\n- [ ] 内存超限：`node -e \"let a=[]; while(1) a.push('x'.repeat(1e6))\"` → OOM，重试3次后进入 DEAD_LETTER\n- [ ] 输出刷屏：`for i in {1..100000}; do echo $i; done` → 终端只显示最后1KB，完整日志存文件\n- [ ] 命令注入：`ls ../../../etc/passwd` → 被安全网关拒绝\n- [ ] 路径遍历：`cat /etc/passwd` → 拒绝（不在白名单目录）\n- [ ] 并发限制：同时提交10个任务 → 只有3个运行，其余排队\n- [ ] 上下文压缩：连续发送50条长消息 → 自动压缩，摘要写入记忆\n- [ ] 主循环卡死模拟：在代码中加入 `while(true);` → 15秒后 process.exit，systemd 重启\n- [ ] 磁盘满模拟：`dd if=/dev/zero of=/tmp/bigfile bs=1M count=5000` → 自动清理旧临时文件，新任务被暂停\n\n---\n\n## 五、总结\n\n**v8.0 最终版本特点**：\n\n| 维度 | 实现要点 | 验证状态 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| **确保执行** | 持久化队列、租约、重试、死信、幂等检查 | ✅ 通过推理 |\n| **防卡死** | 超时、无产出检测、内存限制、输出截断 | ✅ 通过推理 |\n| **安全性** | 命令白名单、路径沙箱、降权、脱敏、限流 | ✅ 通过推理 |\n| **上下文保护** | 多维度触发、增量token、记忆存储 | ✅ 通过推理 |\n| **效率** | 批量提交、缓冲写入、自适应轮询、增量计数 | ✅ 通过推理 |\n| **自愈** | 健康检查、磁盘监控、systemd重启 | ✅ 通过推理 |"}],"timestamp":1775327897814}}
{"type":"message","id":"b29e6322","parentId":"65b279f4","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:39:22.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我学习这个 v4.3 规范。这是一个更完整、更优化的版本，包含了很多我在之前实现中没有完全覆盖的内容。让我分析一下：\n\n新增/改进的点：\n1. **安全网关** - 命令白名单、路径沙箱、限流（这个是之前没有的）\n2. **SQLite WAL 持久化** - 比内存队列更可靠\n3. **租约机制** - 防止任务丢失\n4. **自适应轮询** - 空闲时退避\n5. **权限降级** - uid/gid=nobody\n6. **更好的检查点** - 支持立即 fsync\n7. **增量 token 计数** - 滑动窗口\n8. **磁盘空间监控** - 自动清理\n\n让我把这个整合到保护层中。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n收到！v4.3 是一个非常完整的方案，包含了很多新的改进点。让我学习并整合：\n\n## 评分\n\n| 维度 | 评分 |\n|------|------|\n| 复杂度 | 3分（新模块多） |\n| 不确定性 | 1分（本地代码） |\n| **总分** | **4分** |\n| **路由** | **拆步骤存档** |\n\n---\n\n## 新增改进点对比\n\n| v4.2 | v4.3 新增 | 优先级 |\n|------|-----------|--------|\n| 基础并发 | **SQLite WAL持久化** | 高 |\n| 简单队列 | **租约机制** | 高 |\n| 基础限流 | **IP级别令牌桶** | 高 |\n| 命令验证 | **白名单+路径沙箱** | 高 |\n| 基础超时 | **自适应轮询** | 中 |\n| 固定并发 | **动态调整+空闲退避** | 中 |\n| 无权限降级 | **uid/gid=nobody** | 中 |\n| 基础检查点 | **立即fsync选项** | 中 |\n\n---\n\n让我先把核心新增模块加入：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d59c98e42a91bec88cd1969a07b3e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * OpenCLaw 保护层 - 安全网关\n * v4.3 新增\n * \n * 功能：\n * - IP级别限流（令牌桶）\n * - 命令白名单\n * - 路径沙箱\n * - 任务规格大小限制\n * - 敏感信息脱敏\n */\n\nimport * as fs from 'fs';\nimport * as path from 'path';\n\nclass SecurityGate {\n  constructor(options = {}) {\n    // IP限流配置\n    this.rateLimitPerSec = parseInt(process.env.RATE_LIMIT_PER_SEC || '2');\n    this.tokens = new Map();\n    \n    // 命令白名单\n    this.allowedCommands = (process.env.ALLOWED_COMMANDS || '/usr/bin/ls,/usr/bin/cat,/usr/bin/grep').split(',');\n    \n    // 规格大小限制 (1MB)\n    this.maxSpecSize = parseInt(process.env.MAX_SPEC_SIZE_BYTES || '1048576');\n    \n    // 允许的输入路径前缀\n    this.allowedInputPath = process.env.ALLOWED_INPUT_PATH || '/tmp/openclaw/inputs/';\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * IP限流检查\n   */\n  rateLimit(ip) {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    let entry = this.tokens.get(ip);\n    if (!entry) {\n      entry = { tokens: this.rateLimitPerSec, lastRefill: now };\n      this.tokens.set(ip, entry);\n    }\n    const elapsed = (now - entry.lastRefill) / 1000;\n    entry.tokens = Math.min(this.rateLimitPerSec, entry.tokens + elapsed * this.rateLimitPerSec);\n    entry.lastRefill = now;\n    \n    if (entry.tokens >= 1) {\n      entry.tokens -= 1;\n      return true;\n    }\n    throw new Error('Rate limit exceeded');\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 验证命令（白名单）\n   */\n  async validateCommand(cmd) {\n    // 解析绝对路径\n    let resolved;\n    try {\n      resolved = await fs.realpath(cmd);\n    } catch {\n      throw new Error(`Command not found: ${cmd}`);\n    }\n    \n    if (!this.allowedCommands.includes(resolved)) {\n      throw new Error(`Command not allowed: ${cmd}`);\n    }\n    return true;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 验证路径（沙箱）\n   */\n  validatePath(arg) {\n    // 禁止路径遍历\n    if (arg.includes('..')) {\n      throw new Error(`Path traversal forbidden: ${arg}`);\n    }\n    // 禁止绝对路径（除了允许的输入目录）\n    if (arg.startsWith('/') && !arg.startsWith(this.allowedInputPath)) {\n      throw new Error(`Absolute path not allowed: ${arg}`);\n    }\n    return true;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 验证参数\n   */\n  validateArgs(args) {\n    for (const arg of args || []) {\n      this.validatePath(arg);\n    }\n    return true;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 规格大小限制\n   */\n  validateSpecSize(spec) {\n    const size = JSON.stringify(spec).length;\n    if (size > this.maxSpecSize) {\n      throw new Error(`Spec size ${size} exceeds limit ${this.maxSpecSize}`);\n    }\n    return true;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 敏感信息脱敏（用于日志）\n   */\n  sanitizeSpec(spec) {\n    const sensitive = ['password', 'token', 'secret', 'api_key', 'Authorization'];\n    let str = JSON.stringify(spec);\n    \n    for (const s of sensitive) {\n      // 替换 \"password\": \"xxx\" 为 \"password\": \"***\"\n      const re = new RegExp(`\"(${s})\"\\\\s*:\\\\s*\"[^\"]*\"`, 'gi');\n      str = str.replace(re, `\"$1\":\"***\"`);\n    }\n    \n    try {\n      return JSON.parse(str);\n    } catch {\n      return { _sanitized: true };\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 统一验证\n   */\n  async validate(taskSpec, ip = 'unknown') {\n    // 1. IP限流\n    this.rateLimit(ip);\n    \n    // 2. 规格大小\n    this.validateSpecSize(taskSpec);\n    \n    // 3. 命令验证\n    if (taskSpec.cmd) {\n      await this.validateCommand(taskSpec.cmd);\n    }\n    \n    // 4. 参数验证\n    if (taskSpec.args) {\n      this.validateArgs(taskSpec.args);\n    }\n    \n    return true;\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 获取状态\n   */\n  getStatus() {\n    return {\n      rateLimitPerSec: this.rateLimitPerSec,\n      allowedCommands: this.allowedCommands.length,\n      maxSpecSize: this.maxSpecSize,\n      activeIPs: this.tokens.size\n    };\n  }\n}\n\n// 导出单例\nexport const securityGate = new SecurityGate();\n\nexport default securityGate;","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/protection/security_gate.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":18869,"output":1484,"cacheRead":133888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":154241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775327897818,"responseId":"019d59c933ba443594863fe4d677f20e"}}
