{"type":"message","id":"8d612029","parentId":"caeab4da","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:40:10.707Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d59cb999c035d47235d180a5f79bf","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * OpenCLaw 保护层 - 主入口 (v4.2)\n * \n * 整合所有保护模块，提供统一的 API\n * \n * 模块：\n * - limiter: 并发限制 + 队列\n * - timeout: 超时 + 无产出检测\n * - truncation: 输出截断存储\n * - memory: 内存限制 + OOM 处理\n * - checkpoint: 检查点 + 恢复\n * - summarize: 会话自动压缩\n * - context_protector: 多维度上下文保护\n * - circuit_breaker: 熔断器与限流\n * \n * 使用方式：\n * import protection from './protection/index.js';\n * \n * // 初始化\n * await protection.init();\n * \n * // 提交任务\n * const taskId = protection.submitTask({ spec: myTask });\n * \n * // 执行带保护的任务\n * await protection.runProtected(taskId, async () => {\n *   // 你的任务逻辑\n * });\n */\n\n\n[227 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775328010703}}
