{"type":"message","id":"ef3b9163","parentId":"78ba26d9","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:53:31.140Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题找到了！Gateway 只监听 127.0.0.1 (loopback)，飞书无法从外部连接进来。\n\n需要把 gateway 改为监听 0.0.0.0 或者修改 bind 配置。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 问题找到了！\n\n```\nGateway 监听: 127.0.0.1:18789 (仅本地)\n飞书需要: 从外部连接，但被阻止\n```\n\n**解决方案**：修改 gateway 配置为监听 0.0.0.0\n\n```bash\n# 方案1: 修改配置\nopenclaw config set gateway.bind \"0.0.0.0\"\n\n# 然后重启\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者你说一下你想怎么配置，我来帮你改 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":162733,"output":149,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":162882,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775328786164,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9d2c7efc-410e-4715-87ba-49545af86bae"}}
