{"type":"message","id":"b8f4fb98","parentId":"4253578c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:59:46.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想知道飞书连接问题的最优解决方案。让我快速评分，然后给出答案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 评分\n\n| 维度 | 评分 |\n|------|------|\n| 复杂度 | 1分（配置修改） |\n| 不确定性 | 0分（已知问题） |\n| **总分** | **1分** |\n| **路由** | **直接执行** |\n\n---\n\n## 最优解\n\n**问题**：Gateway 只监听 127.0.0.1，飞书从外部发消息进不来\n\n**方案**：\n\n| 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **A. 改 bind 为 0.0.0.0** | 简单，外部可直接访问 | 需要防火墙配合 |\n| **B. 用 Tailscale 组网** | 安全，内网穿透 | 需要搭建 |\n| **C. 端口转发** | 不改配置 | 需要 nginx/nginx 反向代理 |\n\n**推荐方案 A**：\n\n```bash\n# 一行命令\nopenclaw config set gateway.bind \"0.0.0.0\" && openclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n要执行吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1904,"output":239,"cacheRead":165504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":167647,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775329163777,"responseId":"019d59dd3956d699dd663edaff8ccaf4"}}
