{"type":"message","id":"59034cd7","parentId":"a86ed33a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:03:27.093Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有日志。可能 webhook 请求根本没到达。问题很可能是 Gateway 只监听 127.0.0.1，飞书服务器无法连接。\n\n但飞书用的是 webhook 回调方式，应该不需要 Gateway 开放。让我看看飞书的连接模式。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e08199277cb8400b882b3f60","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查飞书连接模式 ===\" && cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | grep -A 5 '\"feishu\"' | grep -E \"connectionMode|webhook\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":163786,"output":112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":163898,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775329402982,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6dc1bb45-7aa6-4a46-ba64-531438ad638d"}}
