{"type":"message","id":"cee45dd8","parentId":"871c894a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:03:57.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"飞书使用的是 websocket 模式！websocket 需要 Gateway 对外暴露。连接模式有：- websocket：需要 Gateway 对外开放\n- webhook：被动接收\n\n当前是 websocket，所以需要 Gateway 开放才能让飞书连接进来。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d59e146de3bd0a0794132533423b3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 对比连接模式 ===\" && echo \"\n飞书配置: connectionMode = websocket\n\n这意味着:\n- 飞书客户端需要主动连接 Gateway\n- Gateway 必须对外开放 (0.0.0.0)\n- 当前只监听 127.0.0.1，所以飞书连不上\n\nWebhook 模式 vs Websocket 模式:\n- webhook: 被动接收，飞书主动推送 (不需要开放)\n- websocket: 主动连接，需要 Gateway 暴露 (必须改)\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":152348,"output":173,"cacheRead":11520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164041,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775329407117,"responseId":"019d59e0ef223ba8fb4305230c008b04"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4d26468","parentId":"cee45dd8","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:03:57.132Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d59e146de3bd0a0794132533423b3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 对比连接模式 ===\n\n飞书配置: connectionMode = websocket\n\n这意味着:\n- 飞书客户端需要主动连接 Gateway\n- Gateway 必须对外开放 (0.0.0.0)\n- 当前只监听 127.0.0.1，所以飞书连不上\n\nWebhook 模式 vs Websocket 模式:\n- webhook: 被动接收，飞书主动推送 (不需要开放)\n- websocket: 主动连接，需要 Gateway 暴露 (必须改)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"=== 对比连接模式 ===\n\n飞书配置: connectionMode = websocket\n\n这意味着:\n- 飞书客户端需要主动连接 Gateway\n- Gateway 必须对外开放 (0.0.0.0)\n- 当前只监听 127.0.0.1，所以飞书连不上\n\nWebhook 模式 vs Websocket 模式:\n- webhook: 被动接收，飞书主动推送 (不需要开放)\n- websocket: 主动连接，需要 Gateway 暴露 (必须改)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775329437127}}
{"type":"message","id":"db9236c2","parentId":"d4d26468","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:04:27.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在问题很清楚了。总结一下问题和解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 问题原因\n\n```\nconnectionMode: websocket  → 飞书需要主动连接 Gateway\nGateway 监听: 127.0.0.1   → 拒绝外部连接\n→ 结果：飞书连不上\n```\n\n## 两个解决方案\n\n| 方案 | 操作 | 安全性 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| **A. 改 websocket 为 webhook** | 被动接收，无需开放 | 最安全 ✅ |\n| **B. 改 bind 为 0.0.0.0** | 开放 Gateway | 需要加 token/IP限制 |\n\n---\n\n**推荐方案 A**（改 webhook），要执行吗？\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.connectionMode \"webhook\"\nopenclaw gateway restart\n``` 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":151866,"output":167,"cacheRead":12288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164321,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775329437134,"responseId":"019d59e163ebaca8208a3fdd8fb49862"}}
