{"type":"message","id":"11096ec6","parentId":"157bf25c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:06:13.772Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问改配置的影响。让我分析一下。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 评分\n\n| 维度 | 评分 |\n|------|------|\n| 复杂度 | 1分（解释影响） |\n| 不确定性 | 0分 |\n| **总分** | **1分** |\n| **路由** | **直接执行** |\n\n---\n\n## 影响对比\n\n| 影响项 | websocket (当前) | webhook (改后) |\n|--------|-----------------|----------------|\n| **连接方式** | 飞书主动连Gateway | 飞书推送消息给Gateway |\n| **实时性** | 更实时 | 稍有延迟（可忽略） |\n| **Gateway暴露** | 需要 (0.0.0.0) | 不需要 (127.0.0.1) |\n| **断线重连** | 自动 | 自动 |\n| **消息丢失** | 更少 | 几乎无 |\n\n## 总结\n\n| | websocket | webhook |\n|--|-----------|---------|\n| 优点 | 实时 | 安全、简单 |\n| 缺点 | 需要暴露 | 稍微不如websocket实时 |\n\n**对用户来说没区别**，消息都能正常收到。\n\n要改吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3179,"output":243,"cacheRead":164864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":168286,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775329555483,"responseId":"019d59e33131a4419ee1a5f2bba77970"}}
