{"type":"message","id":"d96fb928","parentId":"632bb6b6","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:24:53.170Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d59f3fca028368f8edb133973b831","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 检查现有 on-message hook ===\n#!/bin/bash\nif echo \"$OPENCLAW_MESSAGE\" | grep -qiE \"不对|应该|改成|不要|换成\"; then\n  TIMESTAMP=$(date -Iseconds)\n  mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings\n  echo \"## $TIMESTAMP\" >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md\n  echo \"- Correction: $OPENCLAW_MESSAGE\" >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md\n  echo \"\" >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md\nfi\n\n=== 检查 internal hooks ===\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"internal\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"entries\": {\n        \"session-memory\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"command-logger\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"self-improvement\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  },"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":18,"aggregated":"=== 检查现有 on-message hook ===\n#!/bin/bash\nif echo \"$OPENCLAW_MESSAGE\" | grep -qiE \"不对|应该|改成|不要|换成\"; then\n  TIMESTAMP=$(date -Iseconds)\n  mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings\n  echo \"## $TIMESTAMP\" >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md\n  echo \"- Correction: $OPENCLAW_MESSAGE\" >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md\n  echo \"\" >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md\nfi\n\n=== 检查 internal hooks ===\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"internal\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"entries\": {\n        \"session-memory\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"command-logger\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"self-improvement\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  },","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775330693160}}
{"type":"message","id":"845fd7da","parentId":"d96fb928","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:24:58.210Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！OpenClaw 已经有 hooks 系统了：- `~/.openclaw/hooks/` 目录下有 `on-message.sh` 脚本- 环境变量 `$OPENCLAW_MESSAGE` 包含消息内容- 支持 bash 脚本\n\n我可以创建一个类似 `on-message.sh` 的脚本来调用保护层的接口！\n\n但问题是：这是 bash 脚本，而保护层是 Node.js 模块。需要一种方式让 bash 调用 Node.js。\n\n方案：\n1. 创建一个 Node.js 服务，监听某个端口\n2. 在 bash hook 中 curl 调用这个服务\n3. 或者直接修改 hooks 为 JS 文件\n\n让我看看有没有更简单的方式，比如支持 JS hook。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_45e5d07e5c2b4d30bcd7b18a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查 hook 支持的类型 ===\" && cat ~/.openclaw/hooks/HOOK.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":128271,"output":177,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128448,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775330693173,"responseId":"chatcmpl-47641017-92af-90ba-bd78-872f49c68a40"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa856580","parentId":"845fd7da","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:24:58.235Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_45e5d07e5c2b4d30bcd7b18a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 检查 hook 支持的类型 ===\n---\nname: self-improvement\ndescription: \"Injects self-improvement reminder during agent bootstrap\"\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"🧠\",\"events\":[\"agent:bootstrap\"]}}\n---\n\n# Self-Improvement Hook\n\nInjects a reminder to evaluate learnings during agent bootstrap.\n\n## What It Does\n\n- Fires on `agent:bootstrap` (before workspace files are injected)\n- Adds a reminder block to check `.learnings/` for relevant entries\n- Prompts the agent to log corrections, errors, and discoveries\n\n## Configuration\n\nNo configuration needed. Enable with:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw hooks enable self-improvement\n```"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8,"aggregated":"=== 检查 hook 支持的类型 ===\n---\nname: self-improvement\ndescription: \"Injects self-improvement reminder during agent bootstrap\"\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"🧠\",\"events\":[\"agent:bootstrap\"]}}\n---\n\n# Self-Improvement Hook\n\nInjects a reminder to evaluate learnings during agent bootstrap.\n\n## What It Does\n\n- Fires on `agent:bootstrap` (before workspace files are injected)\n- Adds a reminder block to check `.learnings/` for relevant entries\n- Prompts the agent to log corrections, errors, and discoveries\n\n## Configuration\n\nNo configuration needed. Enable with:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw hooks enable self-improvement\n```","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775330698231}}
