{"type":"message","id":"cbc8de3e","parentId":"a23385d6","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:25:22.882Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是 CLI hooks 相关的代码。看起来 hooks 主要是通过 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 配置的。让我看一下实际的事件触发在哪里。\n\n不过，最简单的方法可能是：使用现有的 `on-message.sh` bash hook，然后通过 curl 调用一个简单的 HTTP 端点来触发保护层。\n\n或者更简单的方法：让我创建一个新的 hook JS 文件，参考 self-improvement.js 的格式（虽然它是空的）。\n\n让我看看有没有更简单的方式 - 先尝试用 bash hook 加上 curl 调用本地服务。\n\n实际上，最简单的方式可能是：在收到飞书消息时（用户消息），我手动调用一次 `global.openclaw.addContextMessage`。这样可以立刻生效，虽然不是全自动的，但可以解决问题。\n\n让我先告诉用户当前的选项。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0cccd18a14c9436fae79c157","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 分析结果 ===\" && echo \"\nOpenClaw Hooks 系统:\n- 支持: JS hook (self-improvement.js) 和 Shell hook (on-message.sh)\n- 配置位置: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json -> hooks.internal.entries\n- 消息环境变量: \\$OPENCLAW_MESSAGE\n\n现有 hook:\n- on-message.sh: 检查消息中是否有纠正词\n- self-improvement.js: 空文件\n\n结论: 可以创建新的 JS hook 或修改 on-message.sh\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":129676,"output":270,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129946,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775330717883,"responseId":"chatcmpl-50b349df-ecc2-4df6-b111-7d1a1f82e960"}}
