{"type":"message","id":"fb2ca411","parentId":"497ef666","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:25:55.535Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我继续实施。最简单的方式是：\n1. 创建一个新的 bash hook 来调用保护层\n2. 或者用 curl 调用一个本地服务\n\n由于 JS hook 的格式不清楚，让我先创建一个简单的 bash hook，通过 curl 调用一个本地服务。或者，更实用的方法：直接用 `on-message.sh` 触发一个本地 HTTP 请求。但由于保护层的上下文模块是在 Node.js 里运行的，需要一个服务来接收请求。最简单的方法：创建一个简单的 HTTP 服务器，监听本地端口，接收消息后调用保护层。但这太复杂了。让我先告诉用户当前的情况，并提供一个手动但有效的方案：在每次收到消息时自动调用保护层。实际上，飞书消息是通过 webhook 发送到 Gateway 的，所以 Gateway 应该能捕获到消息。让我检查一下是否有更简单的方式。\n\n先看看有没有其他方式，比如利用现有的 self-improvement hook。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d59f5489fa455e985180f481d0280","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Context Hook - 自动记录上下文\n# 当收到用户消息时自动调用保护层\n\n# 获取消息内容\nMESSAGE=\"${OPENCLAW_MESSAGE:-}\"\nUSER=\"${OPENCLAW_SENDER:-unknown}\"\nCHANNEL=\"${OPENCLAW_CHANNEL:-unknown}\"\n\nif [ -n \"$MESSAGE\" ]; then\n  # 调用保护层的上下文接口（如果正在运行）\n  # 这里假设有一个 HTTP 服务在运行\n  curl -s -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18790/api/context/add \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"$MESSAGE\\\",\\\"user\\\":\\\"$USER\\\",\\\"channel\\\":\\\"$CHANNEL\\\"}\" \\\n    2>/dev/null || true\n    \n  # 记录日志\n  echo \"[ContextHook] 用户消息已记录: ${MESSAGE:0:50}...\"\nfi","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/on-context.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":10288,"output":400,"cacheRead":119680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130368,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775330722909,"responseId":"019d59f4fffc789bc3952f72f59d281c"}}
