{"type":"message","id":"ce8eb517","parentId":"71dcc613","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:28:34.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来hooks系统有点复杂。让我查看hooks是如何被加载和触发的，可能需要查看runtime文件或者hooks处理相关的代码。\n\n实际上，我意识到一个问题：hook文件应该需要在特定的位置，而且需要检查当前的hook加载机制。从之前的分析，hook可能需要特定的事件类型匹配。\n\n让我采用一个更简单的方式：直接用shell hook，修改现有的 on-message.sh 来同时调用保护层接口。\n\n这样更直接，因为我们知道on-message.sh确实会被调用（当收到消息时）。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d59f7e86d77471cac167a20f72215","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查 openclaw hooks 命令 ===\" && which openclaw && openclaw hooks --help 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3169,"output":148,"cacheRead":129920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133237,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775330902354,"responseId":"019d59f7c1e0899b44ca1883631ce34d"}}
