{"type":"message","id":"a53d63de","parentId":"4ed41dc9","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:28:38.857Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"openclaw命令不可用。让我用更简单的方式 - 直接修改 on-message.sh 来调用保护层。虽然这不是最优方案，但可以工作。\n\n或者，我可以查看on-message.sh是如何被调用的，然后找到更简单的接入点。\n\n从之前的内容，on-message.sh检查OPENCLAW_MESSAGE环境变量。这意味着它会在收到消息时被调用。\n\n让我修改 on-message.sh 来同时记录上下文。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f2ef6596969141f8a6377313","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 查看当前 on-message.sh ===\" && cat ~/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":133362,"output":122,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775330914943,"responseId":"chatcmpl-885054d8-c81f-43aa-b90f-d41830d2a342"}}
