{"type":"message","id":"1322750d","parentId":"33fec6df","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:37:04.067Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！关键代码：```javascript\ntriggerInternalHook(createInternalHookEvent(\"message\", \"received\", sessionKey, {...\n```\n\n这意味着当收到消息时，会触发`message:received`事件。\n\n让我搜索看看有什么hooks被注册到这个事件上。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_768af27b1f4b4481813cb2be","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 分析 Hook 注册 ===\" && echo \"\n关键发现:\n- 消息接收时触发: triggerInternalHook(createInternalHookEvent('message', 'received', ...))\n- 消息发送时触发: triggerInternalHook(createInternalHookEvent('message', 'sent', ...))\n\n事件类型:\n- message:received (用户发送消息)\n- message:sent (AI发送消息)\n\n配置中的 internal.entries.context_hook 应该会注册到这些事件\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":115338,"output":169,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115507,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775331420524,"responseId":"chatcmpl-908f9f79-c495-4132-a995-a7d442fdf609"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad45491e","parentId":"1322750d","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:37:04.098Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_768af27b1f4b4481813cb2be","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 分析 Hook 注册 ===\n\n关键发现:\n- 消息接收时触发: triggerInternalHook(createInternalHookEvent('message', 'received', ...))\n- 消息发送时触发: triggerInternalHook(createInternalHookEvent('message', 'sent', ...))\n\n事件类型:\n- message:received (用户发送消息)\n- message:sent (AI发送消息)\n\n配置中的 internal.entries.context_hook 应该会注册到这些事件"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7,"aggregated":"=== 分析 Hook 注册 ===\n\n关键发现:\n- 消息接收时触发: triggerInternalHook(createInternalHookEvent('message', 'received', ...))\n- 消息发送时触发: triggerInternalHook(createInternalHookEvent('message', 'sent', ...))\n\n事件类型:\n- message:received (用户发送消息)\n- message:sent (AI发送消息)\n\n配置中的 internal.entries.context_hook 应该会注册到这些事件","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775331424090}}
{"type":"message","id":"92ddd493","parentId":"ad45491e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:37:08.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我知道事件类型了。让我检查一下context-hook.js是否正确监听了这些事件。\n\n但问题是，OpenClaw的hooks配置是JSON格式，可能不支持直接注册JS handler到内部hooks事件。让我看看实际的实现方式。\n\n也许我需要在保护层中添加一个简单的直接监听，当Gateway启动时就注册到internal-hooks系统？但这可能太复杂了。\n\n让我换个思路 - 直接在context_inject.js中添加轮询，定期从OpenClaw的某些API获取消息历史。\n\n或者更简单的方案 - 看看OpenClaw是否暴露了消息API。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0f998adf17454fe780c6201c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查 OpenClaw 是否有消息 API ===\" && grep -rn \"getMessages\\|session.*history\\|getContext\" /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/*.js 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"export\\|function\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":115610,"output":210,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115820,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775331424101,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4790c5d5-6fb8-44fe-91fa-5d44af22c40d"}}
