{"type":"message","id":"febbf411","parentId":"8be785bc","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:45:44.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HTTP 服务已启动。现在检查 Hook 接入状态。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 接入状态\n\n| 组件 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **v5 评分系统** | ✅ | task_scorer.js 已完成 |\n| **HTTP 服务** | ✅ | 监听 18790 端口 |\n| **Hook 接入** | ⚠️ | 已修改但 Gateway 可能未触发 |\n| **上下文自动记录** | ⚠️ | 需要 Gateway 触发 Hook |\n\n---\n\n## 问题\n\n**Hook 没有被 Gateway 触发**（Webhook 模式可能不触发 shell hooks）\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案\n\n| 方案 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| **继续调试 Hook** | 需要研究 Gateway 源码 |\n| **手动调用** | ✅ 每次对话后调用 |\n| **换回 websocket 模式** | 需要暴露 Gateway |\n\n**现在先用手动调用方案吧**，你发消息后我帮你记录进去。\n\n或者你想继续调试 Hook？ 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":126740,"output":210,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126950,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775331939912,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3652cb58-55e2-4e67-a0aa-6796f3f27633"}}
