{"type":"message","id":"2d6c0d99","parentId":"beb9f4b3","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:47:01.677Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我解释两个概念：\n1. Hook 接入\n2. 上下文自动记录\n\n让我简单解释一下。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 评分\n\n| 维度 | 评分 |\n|------|------|\n| 复杂度 | 0分（解释概念） |\n| 不确定性 | 0分 |\n| **总分** | **0分** |\n| **路由** | **直接执行** |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Hook 接入\n\n**目的**：让 OpenClaw 在收到消息时自动调用保护层\n\n**当前状态**：\n- ✅ 已修改 `~/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh`\n- ✅ Hook 会调用 HTTP 服务\n- ❌ Gateway 没有触发 Hook（可能 webhook 模式不支持）\n\n**流程**：\n```\n用户发消息 → Gateway收到 → 触发 on-message.sh → 写入队列 → 保护层处理\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. 上下文自动记录\n\n**目的**：记录对话历史，在超过阈值时自动压缩\n\n**当前状态**：\n- ✅ context_protector 模块已实现\n- ✅ 消息队列处理器已启动\n- ❌ 没有消息进入队列（因为 Hook 没触发）\n\n**触发条件**：\n- 消息数 ≥ 50\n- 字符数 ≥ 100KB\n- Token ≥ 80%\n\n---\n\n## 总结\n\n| 概念 | 现状 |\n|------|------|\n| **Hook 接入** | 代码已改，但 Gateway 不触发 |\n| **自动记录** | 机制已就绪，但没消息进来 |\n\n**根本问题**：Gateway 的 Webhook 模式没有调用 hooks 目录的脚本\n\n---\n\n**要继续调试 Hook 触发逻辑，还是先用手动方案？** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":126917,"output":349,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127266,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775332015177,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0e1846e5-6bae-4620-bf15-c9285310e94a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d20ab8e","parentId":"2d6c0d99","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:51:26.328Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 03:51 GMT+8] 学习：# OpenClaw 上下文保护接入方案 B（反向代理中间件）最优解 v2.0\n\n> 本方案通过 **轻量级反向代理中间件** 拦截 Gateway 的 Webhook 请求，在不修改 OpenClaw 源码的前提下，将用户消息同步注入上下文保护层，同时保持原有请求链路不变。 \n> **五维评估**：科学性、鲁棒性、灵活性、可嵌入性、效率性均达到最优。\n\n---\n\n## 一、总体架构\n\n```\n┌─────────┐ ┌──────────────────────┐ ┌─────────────┐ ┌──────────┐\n│ 用户 │────▶│ 反向代理中间件 │────▶│ OpenClaw │────▶│ Agent │\n│ │ │ (Express + Proxy) │ │ Gateway │ │ │\n└─────────┘ └──────────┬───────────┘ └─────────────┘ └──────────┘\n │\n │ HTTP POST /api/context/message\n ▼\n ┌─────────────┐\n │ 上下文保护层 │\n │ (独立服务) │\n └─────────────┘\n```\n\n- **用户请求**：发送到中间件地址（如 `http://localhost:3002/webhook`）。\n- **中间件**：\n 1. 解析请求体，提取 `message`、`userId`、`taskId`。\n 2. **异步**调用上下文保护层 API（不阻塞主流程）。\n 3. 将原始请求**透传**给 OpenClaw Gateway。\n- **上下文保护层**：\n - 提供 HTTP 接口 `/api/context/message` 接收消息。\n - 维护消息队列、触发自动压缩、写入长期记忆。\n\n---\n\n## 二、五维设计评估\n\n| 维度 | 设计要点 | 评价 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **科学性** | 采用异步非阻塞模式，保护层调用失败不影响主链路；消息记录与 AI 处理解耦，符合关注点分离原则。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **鲁棒性** | 保护层 API 调用失败时仅记录错误，不重试（避免放大故障）；中间件自身健康检查；超时保护（2 秒）。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **灵活性** | 支持配置保护层地址、超时时间、是否启用；可动态添加更多中间件逻辑（如日志、限流）。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **可嵌入性** | 中间件独立部署，不修改 OpenClaw 任何源码；通过环境变量配置 Gateway 地址和保护层地址。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **效率性** | 异步调用 + 短超时（2 秒）几乎不增加主链路延迟；使用 Keep-Alive 连接池复用。 | ✅ 高 |\n\n---\n\n## 三、完整伪代码实现\n\n### 3.1 中间件服务（`context-middleware.js`）\n\n```javascript\n// context-middleware.js\n// 反向代理中间件，拦截 Webhook 请求，转发给上下文保护层和 OpenClaw Gateway\n\nconst express = require('express');\nconst { createProxyMiddleware } = require('http-proxy-middleware');\nconst axios = require('axios');\n\n// ========== 配置区（支持环境变量） ==========\nconst PORT = process.env.MIDDLEWARE_PORT || 3002;\nconst GATEWAY_URL = process.env.OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL || 'http://localhost:3000';\nconst CONTEXT_API_URL = process.env.CONTEXT_API_URL || 'http://localhost:3001/api/context/message';\nconst CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS = parseInt(process.env.CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS || '2000', 10);\nconst ENABLE_CONTEXT = process.env.ENABLE_CONTEXT !== 'false'; // 默认启用\n\n// ========== 创建 Express 应用 ==========\nconst app = express();\napp.use(express.json({ limit: '1mb' })); // 限制请求体大小\n\n// ========== 健康检查端点 ==========\napp.get('/health', (req, res) => {\n res.json({ status: 'ok', timestamp: Date.now() });\n});\n\n// ========== 核心拦截逻辑 ==========\napp.post('/webhook', async (req, res, next) => {\n // 1. 提取消息内容（根据 OpenClaw Gateway 的请求格式调整）\n const { message, userId, taskId, text, user } = req.body;\n const content = message || text || (req.body.content) || null;\n const uid = userId || user || 'anonymous';\n const tid = taskId || null;\n\n // 2. 异步调用上下文保护层（不等待，不阻塞）\n if (ENABLE_CONTEXT && content) {\n // 使用 Promise 但立即释放，只记录错误\n axios.post(CONTEXT_API_URL, {\n role: 'user',\n content: content,\n taskId: tid,\n userId: uid,\n timestamp: Date.now()\n }, {\n timeout: CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS,\n // 保持连接复用\n headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }\n }).catch(err => {\n // 静默失败，只打印日志（不抛出异常）\n console.error(`[ContextMiddleware] Failed to record message: ${err.message}`);\n });\n }\n\n // 3. 继续转发到 OpenClaw Gateway（不修改请求）\n next();\n});\n\n// ========== 代理到 OpenClaw Gateway ==========\napp.use('/webhook', createProxyMiddleware({\n target: GATEWAY_URL,\n changeOrigin: true,\n // 可选：日志\n logLevel: 'warn',\n // 错误处理：代理失败时返回 502\n onError: (err, req, res) => {\n console.error(`[Proxy Error] ${err.message}`);\n res.status(502).json({ error: 'Gateway unreachable' });\n }\n}));\n\n// 其他路径也代理过去（可选）\napp.use('/', createProxyMiddleware({ target: GATEWAY_URL, changeOrigin: true }));\n\n// ========== 启动服务 ==========\napp.listen(PORT, () => {\n console.log(`Context middleware listening on port ${PORT}`);\n console.log(`Proxying to Gateway: ${GATEWAY_URL}`);\n console.log(`Context API: ${CONTEXT_API_URL} (timeout ${CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS}ms)`);\n});\n```\n\n### 3.2 上下文保护层 API（扩展 `context_protector.js`）\n\n```javascript\n// context_protector.js (已有模块，增加 HTTP 接口)\n\nconst express = require('express');\nconst bodyParser = require('body-parser');\n\n// 假设已有 ContextProtector 类\nconst contextProtector = require('./context_protector_instance'); // 单例\n\n// 创建 API 服务\nconst apiApp = express();\napiApp.use(bodyParser.json({ limit: '1mb' }));\n\n// 记录消息\napiApp.post('/api/context/message', async (req, res) => {\n try {\n const { role, content, taskId, userId } = req.body;\n if (!content) {\n return res.status(400).json({ error: 'Missing content' });\n }\n await contextProtector.addMessage(role || 'user', content, taskId);\n // 可选：关联 userId 到会话\n res.json({ success: true, messageCount: contextProtector.messageCount() });\n } catch (err) {\n console.error(`[ContextAPI] Error: ${err.message}`);\n res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal error' });\n }\n});\n\n// 获取上下文状态\napiApp.get('/api/context/status', (req, res) => {\n res.json({\n messages: contextProtector.getMessages().length,\n chars: contextProtector.getTotalChars(),\n tokens: contextProtector.getTotalTokens(),\n lastSummarize: contextProtector.getLastSummarize(),\n thresholds: contextProtector.getThresholds()\n });\n});\n\n// 手动触发压缩\napiApp.post('/api/context/summarize', async (req, res) => {\n try {\n await contextProtector.forceSummarize();\n res.json({ success: true });\n } catch (err) {\n res.status(500).json({ error: err.message });\n }\n});\n\n// 回滚\napiApp.post('/api/context/rollback', async (req, res) => {\n const success = await contextProtector.rollback();\n res.json({ success });\n});\n\nconst API_PORT = process.env.CONTEXT_API_PORT || 3001;\napiApp.listen(API_PORT, () => {\n console.log(`Context protector API listening on port ${API_PORT}`);\n});\n```\n\n### 3.3 上下文保护核心类（关键方法）\n\n```javascript\nclass ContextProtector {\n constructor() {\n this.messages = [];\n this.totalChars = 0;\n this.totalTokens = 0;\n this.lastSummarize = 0;\n this.backupHistory = null;\n this.thresholds = {\n msgs: parseInt(process.env.CONTEXT_MSG_THRESHOLD || '50', 10),\n chars: parseInt(process.env.CONTEXT_CHAR_THRESHOLD || '102400', 10),\n tokenRatio: parseFloat(process.env.CONTEXT_TOKEN_RATIO || '0.8'),\n tokenLimit: parseInt(process.env.CONTEXT_TOKEN_LIMIT || '131072', 10),\n cooldownSec: parseInt(process.env.CONTEXT_COOLDOWN_SEC || '120', 10)\n };\n }\n\n // 添加消息（核心）\n async addMessage(role, content, taskId = null) {\n const tokens = this.estimateTokens(content);\n this.messages.push({ role, content, timestamp: Date.now(), taskId, tokens });\n this.totalChars += content.length;\n this.totalTokens += tokens;\n if (this.shouldSummarize()) {\n await this.summarize();\n }\n }\n\n // 判断是否触发压缩\n shouldSummarize() {\n if (Date.now() - this.lastSummarize < this.thresholds.cooldownSec * 1000) return false;\n if (this.messages.length >= this.thresholds.msgs) return true;\n if (this.totalChars >= this.thresholds.chars) return true;\n if (this.totalTokens / this.thresholds.tokenLimit >= this.thresholds.tokenRatio) return true;\n return false;\n }\n\n // 执行压缩（写入记忆，保留最近10条）\n async summarize() {\n const toSummarize = this.messages.slice(0, -10);\n let summary;\n try {\n summary = await this.callSummarizeAPI(toSummarize.map(m => m.content).join('\\n'));\n } catch (err) {\n summary = this.extractKeyInfo(toSummarize);\n }\n // 写入长期记忆（略）\n const memoryId = await this.storeSummary(summary);\n // 保留最近10条 + 系统消息\n this.messages = [\n { role: 'system', content: `[历史摘要已存储，ID: ${memoryId}]`, tokens: 0 },\n ...this.messages.slice(-10)\n ];\n this.totalChars = this.messages.reduce((s, m) => s + (m.content?.length || 0), 0);\n this.totalTokens = this.messages.reduce((s, m) => s + (m.tokens || 0), 0);\n this.lastSummarize = Date.now();\n }\n\n // 估算 token（轻量）\n estimateTokens(text) {\n const ch = (text.match(/[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]/g) || []).length;\n const other = text.length - ch;\n return Math.ceil(ch / 1.5 + other / 4);\n }\n\n // 其他辅助方法...\n}\n```\n\n### 3.4 部署与进程管理（systemd 单元文件）\n\n```ini\n# /etc/systemd/system/openclaw-context.service\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Context Protector API\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=openclaw\nWorkingDirectory=/opt/openclaw\nEnvironment=\"NODE_ENV=production\"\nEnvironment=\"CONTEXT_API_PORT=3001\"\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node /opt/openclaw/context_api.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=10\nLimitNOFILE=65536\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\n```\n\n```ini\n# /etc/systemd/system/openclaw-middleware.service\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Context Middleware\nAfter=network.target openclaw-context.service openclaw-gateway.service\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=openclaw\nEnvironment=\"MIDDLEWARE_PORT=3002\"\nEnvironment=\"OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL=http://localhost:3000\"\nEnvironment=\"CONTEXT_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api/context/message\"\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node /opt/openclaw/context-middleware.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=10\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\n```\n\n### 3.5 环境变量配置（`.env` 或直接导出）\n\n```bash\n# 中间件\nMIDDLEWARE_PORT=3002\nOPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL=http://localhost:3000\nCONTEXT_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api/context/message\nCONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS=2000\nENABLE_CONTEXT=true\n\n# 上下文保护层\nCONTEXT_API_PORT=3001\nCONTEXT_MSG_THRESHOLD=50\nCONTEXT_CHAR_THRESHOLD=102400\nCONTEXT_TOKEN_RATIO=0.8\nCONTEXT_TOKEN_LIMIT=131072\nCONTEXT_COOLDOWN_SEC=120\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、测试验证\n\n### 4.1 启动服务\n\n```bash\n# 启动保护层 API\nnode context_api.js &\n# 启动中间件\nnode context-middleware.js &\n# 确保 OpenClaw Gateway 运行在 3000 端口\n```\n\n### 4.2 发送测试消息\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3002/webhook \\\n -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n -d '{\"message\":\"Hello, OpenClaw!\", \"userId\":\"test_user\"}'\n```\n\n### 4.3 检查上下文状态\n\n```bash\ncurl http://localhost:3001/api/context/status\n```\n\n预期输出：\n```json\n{\"messages\":1,\"chars\":18,\"tokens\":5,\"lastSummarize\":0,\"thresholds\":{...}}\n```\n\n### 4.4 模拟长对话\n\n使用脚本连续发送 60 条消息，观察是否在第 50 条后触发压缩（查看日志或 `/api/context/status` 中 `lastSummarize` 更新）。\n\n---\n\n## 五、鲁棒性增强点\n\n1. **保护层 API 超时**：中间件调用保护层设置 2 秒超时，避免保护层故障阻塞主链路。\n2. **连接池复用**：`axios` 默认使用连接池，减少 TCP 握手开销。\n3. **失败静默**：保护层调用失败仅记录日志，不影响用户请求。\n4. **健康检查**：中间件提供 `/health` 端点，可供负载均衡器探测。\n5. **代理错误处理**：若 Gateway 不可用，返回 502 并记录错误。\n6. **请求体大小限制**：限制 1MB，防止恶意大请求。\n\n---\n\n## 六、灵活性扩展点\n\n- **可插拔**：可通过环境变量 `ENABLE_CONTEXT=false` 完全禁用上下文记录，中间件退化为纯代理。\n- **多 Gateway 支持**：修改 `GATEWAY_URL` 即可切换后端。\n- **自定义消息提取**：根据实际 Gateway 请求格式，调整 `message`、`userId` 的字段名。\n- **支持批量消息**：可扩展为接收数组，一次记录多条消息。\n\n---\n\n## 七、总结\n\n本方案通过 **反向代理中间件** 实现了上下文保护层与 OpenClaw Gateway 的无缝集成，具备：\n\n- **科学性**：异步解耦，保护层故障不影响主业务。\n- **鲁棒性**：超时、重试（仅限连接层）、健康检查、失败静默。\n- **灵活性**：配置化、可插拔、易于扩展。\n- **可嵌入性**：独立部署，不修改 OpenClaw 任何代码，升级无影响。\n- **效率性**：异步调用 + 连接复用，主链路增加延迟 < 5ms（实测）。"}],"timestamp":1775332286300}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d9d0e2a","parentId":"4d20ab8e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:51:42.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我学习这个 v2.0 方案。这个方案是通过反向代理中间件来接入上下文保护层，绕过 Gateway Webhook 模式下 Hook 不触发的问题。\n\n让我评分：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 评分\n\n| 维度 | 评分 |\n|------|------|\n| 复杂度 | 3分（部署中间件+2个服务） |\n| 不确定性 | 1分（需要配置端口） |\n| **总分** | **4分** |\n| **路由** | **spawn子代理** |\n\n---\n\n学习方案 v2.0：\n\n## 核心思路\n\n**问题**：Gateway Webhook 模式不触发 Hook\n\n**解决方案**：用反向代理中间件拦截请求，异步调用保护层\n\n```\n用户 → 中间件(3002) → 转发 Gateway(3000)\n         ↓\n    异步调用保护层(3001)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 实现步骤\n\n1. **部署保护层 API 服务**（端口3001）\n2. **部署中间件服务**（端口3002）\n3. **配置飞书 webhook 到中间件**\n\n---\n\n开始部署：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5a0c8cd9e2d301b4d40ba9051a85","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 方案B：反向代理中间件 ===\" && echo \"\n方案优势:\n- 不修改 OpenClaw 源码\n- 异步调用，不阻塞主流程\n- 失败静默，不影响用户\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4398,"output":294,"cacheRead":125952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130644,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775332286324,"responseId":"019d5a0c5a3b3c22bd7d6f87bc804634"}}
{"type":"message","id":"978733d8","parentId":"3d9d0e2a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:51:42.755Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5a0c8cd9e2d301b4d40ba9051a85","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 方案B：反向代理中间件 ===\n\n方案优势:\n- 不修改 OpenClaw 源码\n- 异步调用，不阻塞主流程\n- 失败静默，不影响用户"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12,"aggregated":"=== 方案B：反向代理中间件 ===\n\n方案优势:\n- 不修改 OpenClaw 源码\n- 异步调用，不阻塞主流程\n- 失败静默，不影响用户","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775332302749}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f93a40d","parentId":"978733d8","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:52:04.525Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在开始部署这个方案。需要：1. 创建一个简单的反向代理中间件2. 已经有了 context_server.js，可以扩展它支持代理功能3. 部署中间件让我先检查当前的 context_server.js 是否已经有类似功能，如果没有就创建一个新的中间件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_14c6f44da95e45659fc3887f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * OpenClaw 上下文中间件 - 反向代理版本 v2.0\n * \n * 拦截 Webhook 请求，转发给 Gateway，同时调用上下文保护层\n * \n * 工作流程:\n * 用户 → POST /webhook → 中间件 → 转发 Gateway\n *                          ↓\n *                    异步调用保护层\n */\n\nimport { createServer } from 'http';\nimport { contextProtector } from './context_protector.js';\nimport { securityGate } from './security_gate.js';\n\nconst PORT = parseInt(process.env.MIDDLEWARE_PORT || '3002');\nconst GATEWAY_URL = process.env.OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL || 'http://127.0.0.1:18789';\nconst CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS = parseInt(process.env.CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS || '2000');\n\nconst server = createServer(async (req, res) => {\n  // CORS\n  res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Origin', '*');\n  res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Methods', 'GET, POST, OPTIONS');\n  res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Headers', 'Content-Type, Authorization');\n  \n  if (req.method === 'OPTIONS') {\n    res.writeHead(200);\n    res.end();\n    return;\n  }\n\n  // 健康检查\n  if (req.url === '/health') {\n    res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n    res.end(JSON.stringify({ status: 'ok', timestamp: Date.now(), service: 'middleware' }));\n    return;\n  }\n\n  // Webhook 拦截\n  if (req.url === '/webhook' && req.method === 'POST') {\n    try {\n      let body = '';\n      for await (const chunk of req) {\n        body += chunk;\n      }\n      \n      let data;\n      try {\n        data = JSON.parse(body);\n      } catch {\n        res.writeHead(400, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n        res.end(JSON.stringify({ error: 'Invalid JSON' }));\n        return;\n      }\n\n      // 提取消息内容（适配飞书格式）\n      const content = data.message || data.text || data.content || data.msg || '';\n      const userId = data.user_id || data.userId || data.sender || 'unknown';\n      const taskId = data.task_id || data.taskId || null;\n\n      // 异步调用上下文保护层（不阻塞）\n      if (content) {\n        this.callContextApi({\n          role: 'user',\n          content: content,\n          taskId: taskId,\n          userId: userId,\n          timestamp: Date.now()\n        }).catch(err => {\n          console.log('[Middleware] 上下文记录失败:', err.message);\n        });\n      }\n\n      // 转发到 Gateway\n      const gatewayReq = require('http').request(GATEWAY_URL + '/webhook', {\n        method: 'POST',\n        headers: {\n          'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n          'X-Forwarded-For': req.socket.remoteAddress\n        }\n      }, (gatewayRes) => {\n        let responseBody = '';\n        gatewayRes.on('data', chunk => responseBody += chunk);\n        gatewayRes.on('end', () => {\n          res.writeHead(gatewayRes.statusCode, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n          res.end(responseBody);\n        });\n      });\n\n      gatewayReq.on('error', (err) => {\n        console.log('[Middleware] Gateway 转发失败:', err.message);\n        res.writeHead(502, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n        res.end(JSON.stringify({ error: 'Gateway unreachable' }));\n      });\n\n      gatewayReq.write(body);\n      gatewayReq.end();\n\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('[Middleware] 处理错误:', error.message);\n      res.writeHead(500, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n      res.end(JSON.stringify({ error: error.message }));\n    }\n    return;\n  }\n\n  // 其他路径也转发到 Gateway\n  if (req.url.startsWith('/')) {\n    const targetUrl = GATEWAY_URL + req.url;\n    \n    const options = {\n      hostname: require('url').parse(targetUrl).hostname,\n      port: require('url').parse(targetUrl).port,\n      path: require('url').parse(targetUrl).path,\n      method: req.method,\n      headers: req.headers\n    };\n\n    const proxyReq = require('http').request(options, (proxyRes) => {\n      res.writeHead(proxyRes.statusCode, proxyRes.headers);\n      proxyRes.pipe(res, { end: true });\n    });\n\n    proxyReq.on('error', (err) => {\n      res.writeHead(502);\n      res.end('Gateway error');\n    });\n\n    req.pipe(proxyReq, { end: true });\n    return;\n  }\n\n  res.writeHead(404);\n  res.end('Not Found');\n});\n\n// 异步调用上下文保护层\nserver.callContextApi = async (msgData) => {\n  try {\n    const response = await fetch('http://127.0.0.1:18790/api/context/add', {\n      method: 'POST',\n      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n      body: JSON.stringify(msgData),\n      signal: AbortSignal.timeout(CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS)\n    });\n    return await response.json();\n  } catch (err) {\n    throw err;\n  }\n};\n\nserver.listen(PORT, () => {\n  console.log(`[Middleware] 反向代理中间件已启动: http://127.0.0.1:${PORT}`);\n  console.log(`[Middleware] Gateway 地址: ${GATEWAY_URL}`);\n  console.log(`[Middleware] 上下文API: http://127.0.0.1:18790`);\n  console.log(`[Middleware] 上下文超时: ${CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS}ms`);\n});\n\nexport default server;","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/protection/middleware.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":130893,"output":1322,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132215,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775332302759,"responseId":"chatcmpl-97afebc2-1b2c-4de0-950b-2f8d79102606"}}
