{"type":"message","id":"84417b64","parentId":"d9eebd14","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:53:51.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我测试一下中间件是否能正常工作，同时说明需要修改飞书webhook地址：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 中间件部署完成！\n\n### 服务状态\n\n| 服务 | 端口 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **中间件** | 3002 | ✅ 运行中 |\n| **上下文API** | 18790 | ✅ 运行中 |\n| **Gateway** | 18789/3000 | ✅ 运行中 |\n\n---\n\n### 下一步：配置飞书 Webhook\n\n**需要修改飞书后台的 Webhook 地址**：\n\n```\n旧地址: https://xxx.openclaw.ai/webhook\n新地址: https://xxx.openclaw.ai:3002/webhook\n```\n\n或者如果 Gateway 已经暴露到公网：\n\n```\n直接地址: http://<你的IP>:3002/webhook\n```\n\n---\n\n### 测试中间件\n\n```bash\n# 测试消息\ncurl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:3002/webhook \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"测试中间件\",\"user_id\":\"test\"}'\n\n# 检查上下文状态\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:18790/api/context/status\n```\n\n---\n\n**你能去飞书后台修改 Webhook 地址吗？** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":132763,"output":268,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775332426433,"responseId":"chatcmpl-638571fa-ed0e-4c63-8826-1e0ca6582b60"}}
